a%20design%20lead%20in%20the%20Google%20Play%20movies%20team%20in%202016.%20I%20was%20fascinated%20with%20how%20technology%20and%20entertainment%20came%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20became%20obsessed%20with%20the%20feeling%20of%20making%20products%20that%20people%20use%20every%20day.%20When%20we%20launched%20something%2C%20it'd%20launch%20it%20to%20hundreds%20of%20millions%2C%20if%20not%20billions%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20the%20design%20lead%20for%20Google%20TV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20there%2C%20a%20few%20folks%20internally%20looked%20at%20the%20landscape%20of%20entertainment%20for%20technology%20and%20saw%20that%20Apple%20TV%20and%20Amazon%20Firestick%20were%20doing%20amazing%20things.%20Google%20didn't%20really%20have%20a%20TV%20offering%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20heard%20some%20people%20were%20thinking%20about%20Google's%20place%20in%20the%20TV%20space%2C%20and%20I%20managed%20to%20join%20in%20with%20that%20team%20on%20the%20side%20of%20my%20main%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20very%20supportive%20manager.%20She%20told%20me%20to%20jump%20onto%20the%20TV%20project%20and%20leave%20her%20team%2C%20even%20though%20hiring%20me%20had%20been%20a%20long%20process.%20She%20really%20looked%20out%20for%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20the%20new%20team%20in%202018%20and%20became%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20designers%20of%20Google%20TV.%20There%20was%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20us.%20We%20started%20with%20ideas%20on%20a%20whiteboard.%20It%20felt%20like%20being%20in%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20on%20it%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%20and%20saw%20the%20product%20launch%20on%20Chromecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20amazing%20to%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20an%20idea%2C%20build%20it%2C%20and%20watch%20it%20go%20big%20really%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20left%20Google%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3