Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fsuperman-legacy-film-date-david-zaslav-slams-flops-1235920304%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20Thieves%20Arrested%20In%20UP%2C%20They%20Stole%20Over%20500%20Cars%20Using%20YouTube%2C%20Software%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20studied%20till%20the%20fifth%20standard%20and%20used%20to%20ride%20an%20autorickshaw%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Raunak%20alias%20Babbu%20and%20planned%20to%20steal%20cars%2C%20from%20there%20on%20the%20duo%20expanded%20their%20gang%20and%20stole%20over%20500%20cars%2C%20including%20several%20luxury%20four-wheelers.%20They%20were%20illiterate%2C%20but%20they%20learnt%20how%20to%20steal%20cars%20from%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaj%20Mohammad%20and%20Raunak%20Ali%20met%20Rinku%20and%20Hakim%20and%20started%20stealing%20cars%20in%20Delhi%20and%20its%20adjoining%20areas.%20They%20went%20to%20jail%20several%20times.%20When%20Taj's%20accomplices%20were%20in%20jail%2C%20he%20started%20his%20gang%20with%20Guddu%2C%20Kashif%20and%20Matin.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20have%20arrested%20the%20gang%20members%20from%20Ghaziabad's%20Mussourie%20and%20uncovered%20the%20nexus%20that%20has%20connections%20with%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gang%20used%20hi-tech%20software%20to%20unlock%20cars.%20The%20thieves%20then%20supplied%20the%20stolen%20cars%20to%20Aamir%20in%20Sambhal%2C%20to%20whom%20they%20delivered%20over%20200%20vehicles%20and%20to%20a%20man%20in%20Vadodara%20Gujarat.%20They%20downloaded%20software%20on%20their%20tablets%20to%20unlock%20luxury%20cars%20that%20have%20an%20anti-theft%20system%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamir%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20an%20accomplice%20in%20the%20theft%20too%2C%20the%20cops%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20couple%20gave%20them%20tools%20to%20steal%20cars%20and%20even%20supplied%20remote-controlled%20car%20keys%2C%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Crime%2C%20Ajit%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoftware%2C%20Duplicate%20Keys%2C%20Magnet%20-%20The%20Modus%20Operandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20the%20police%20that%20they%20steal%20when%20there's%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20car.%20Guddu%2C%20Matin%2C%20and%20Kashif%20go%20on%20a%20recce%20to%20spot%20a%20car.%20The%20gang%20members%2C%20after%20spotting%20a%20car%2C%20used%20to%20break%20the%20lock%20of%20the%20trunk%20or%20smash%20the%20window%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20vehicle%20and%20make%20a%20duplicate%20key%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20software%20they%20downloaded%20on%20their%20tablet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20used%20magnets%20to%20break%20the%20steering%20lock%20of%20the%20cars%2C%20change%20the%20number%20plate%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20remove%20the%20GPS%20trackers%20from%20them.%20As%20technology%20in%20cars%20changes%2C%20their%20modus%20operandi%20changed%20too.%20The%20thieves%20would%20put%20their%20phone%20on%20flight%20time%20and%20disable%20the%20location%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20not%20tracked.%20They%20told%20the%20police%20that%20used%20WhatsApp%20to%20communicate%20and%20avoided%20normal%20calls%20while%20committing%20the%20crime.%20The%20profit%20was%20equally%20divided%20among%20them%20and%20the%20rest%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20lifestyle%20they%20wanted%20to%20live%2C%20which%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20said%20was%20the%20reason%20to%20start%20stealing%20cars.%20The%20police%20said%20they%20preferred%20stealing%20luxury%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Want%20A%20Better%20Lifestyle'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuddu%2C%20who%20never%20went%20to%20school%20and%20used%20to%20ride%20an%20e-rickshaw%2C%20said%20he%20started%20stealing%20cars%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20earn%20more%20and%20have%20a%20good%20lifestyle.%20Others%20had%20similar%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interstate%20nexus%20had%20connections%20with%20Dubai.%20Aamir%20operated%20out