ates%20a%20payments%20bank%20and%20voice%20box%2C%20and%20other%20fintech%20players%20to%20benefit%20as%20Paytm%20will%20struggle%20to%20retain%20its%20merchants%20and%20customers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmukesh-ambani-s-jio-financial-services-market-cap-tops-rs-2-trillion-124022300937_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmukesh-ambani-s-jio-financial-services-market-cap-tops-rs-2-trillion-124022300937_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmukesh-ambani-s-jio-financial-services-market-cap-tops-rs-2-trillion-124022300937_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI's%20New%20Advisory%20On%20Paytm%20UPI%20Payments%3A%20What%20It%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20come%20out%20with%20additional%20measures%20to%20ensure%20seamless%20digital%20transactions%20via%20unified%20payments%20interface%20or%20UPI.%20The%20directions%20apply%20exclusively%20to%20current%20%40paytm%20UPI%20handle%20users.%20No%20action%20is%20required%20for%20those%20using%20UPI%20addresses%20other%20than%20%40paytm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20in%20January%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20(OCL)%20-%20also%20known%20as%20Paytm%2C%20to%20stop%20accepting%20any%20fresh%20deposits%20in%20its%20accounts%2C%20or%20wallets%2C%20from%20February%2029.%20That%20deadline%20was%20extended%20to%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20New%20RBI%20Advisory%20Say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20has%20advised%20the%20payments%20authority%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20to%20examine%20a%20request%20from%20Paytm%20to%20become%20a%20third-party%20application%20provider%20(TPAP).%20for%20UPI%20channel%20for%20continued%20UPI%20operation%20of%20the%20Paytm%20app%2C%20as%20per%20the%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20asked%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20'%40paytm'%20handles%20are%20to%20be%20migrated%20in%20a%20seamless%20manner%20from%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20a%20set%20of%20newly%20identified%20banks%20to%20avoid%20any%20disruption.%20No%20new%20users%20are%20to%20be%20added%20by%20the%20said%20TPAP%20until%20all%20the%20existing%20users%20are%20migrated%20satisfactorily%20to%20a%20new%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20%26quot%3Bseamless%20migration%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20RBI%20has%20asked%20the%20NPCI%20to%20facilitate%20the%20certification%20of%20four%20to%20five%20banks%20as%20Payment%20Service%20Provider%20(PSP)%20Banks%20with%20demonstrated%20capabilities%20to%20process%20high-volume%20UPI%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchants%20using%20Paytm%20QR%20codes%20may%20see%20settlement%20accounts%20opened%20with%20PSP%20banks%20other%20than%20PSP%20banks%20if%20Paytm%20decides%20to%20pursue%20this%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaytm%20Signs%20New%20Banking%20Partner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Paytm%20shifted%20its%20nodal%20account%20to%20Axis%20Bank%20(by%20opening%20an%20escrow%20account)%20to%20continue%20seamless%20merchant%20settlements%20as%20before.%20It%20had%20then%20insisted%20that%20its%20QR%20codes%2C%20soundbox%20and%20card%20machines%20would%20continue%20to%20work%20beyond%20the%20RBI's%20March%2015%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20extension%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20was%20to%20allow%20customers%2C%20including%20merchants%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20more%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20alternative%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERBI's%20FAQs%20Over%20Paytm%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20no%20further%20deposits%20or%20credit%20transactions%20or%20top-ups%20shall%20be%20allowed%20in%20any%20customer%20accounts%2C%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20wallets%2C%20FASTags%2C%20National%20Common%20Mobility%20Cards%2C%20etc%20after%20March%2015%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20withdraw%20or%20use%20funds%20from%20their%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20accounts%20and%20wallets%20until%20the%20time%20those%20funds%20are%20exhausted%20but%20they%20cannot%20add%20any%20fresh%20funds%20after%20March%2015%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20also%20asked%20customers%20who%20get%20their%20salaries%20or%20other%20transfers%20including%20government%20subsidies%20into%20these%20accounts%20to%20make%20alternate%20arrangements%20by%20mid-March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchants%20using%20Paytm's%20QR%20codes%20for%20accepting%20payments%20can%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20if%20these%20QR%20codes%20are%20linked%20to%20accounts%20other%20than%20those%20held%20by%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%20has%20nearly%20a%20fifth%20share%20of%20India's%20toll%20collections%20through%20a%20product%20called%20FASTag.%20The%20RBI%20said%20these%20FASTags%20cannot%20be%20recharged%20or%20topped%20up%20after%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20is%20the%20third%20largest%20app%20for%20UPI%20payments%20in%20the%20country%2C%20processing%201.6%20billion%20monthly%20transactions%2C%20according%20to%20data%20available%20on%20the%20NPCI%20website.%20PhonePe%20and%20Google%20Pay%20are%20the%20two%20largest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Reuters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708695360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F6bpurefg_paytm_625x300_09_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbis-new-advisory-on-paytm-upi-payments-what-it-means-5113807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20come%20out%20with%20additional%20measures%20to%20ensure%20seamless%20digital%20transactions%20via%