20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20communications%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20K.C.%20Venugopal%20had%20written%20to%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20demanding%20a%20court%20monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Ftnm-nl-investigation-30-firms-facing-ed-it-probe-donated-rs-335-cr-to-bjp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20Newslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20found%20that%2030%20firms%20that%20are%20facing%20ED%20and%20IT%20probes%20donated%20Rs%20335%20crores%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20case%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehafta%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3Evasooli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(extortion)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERs%20335%20crore%20to%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20found%20that%20at%20least%2030%20companies%2C%20which%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20nearly%20Rs%20335%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20between%20financial%20years%202018-19%20and%202022-23%2C%20also%20faced%20action%20by%20central%20agencies%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20of%20these%20firms%2C%2023%20companies%2C%20which%20gave%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20187.58%20crore%20to%20the%20party%20during%20this%20period%2C%20had%20never%20donated%20any%20amount%20to%20the%20BJP%20between%202014%20and%20the%20year%20of%20the%20raid%20and%20at%20least%20four%20companies%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%209.05%20crore%20within%20four%20months%20of%20the%20central%20agency%20visit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20found%20that%20at%20least%20six%20of%20these%20firms%2C%20which%20were%20already%20donors%20to%20the%20party%2C%20donated%20a%20larger%20amount%20in%20the%20months%20following%20raids%2C%20while%20six%20other%20firms%2C%20which%20had%20donated%20to%20the%20BJP%20each%20year%20before%2C%20faced%20central%20action%20after%20they%20skipped%20donations%20in%20one%20financial%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20at%20least%20three%20BJP%20donors%2C%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20list%20of%2030%2C%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20receiving%20undue%20favours%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20Only%20three%20of%20these%2032%20companies%20donated%20to%20the%20Congress%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20hafta%20vasooli%20and%20nothing%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGiving%20threats%20through%20CBI%2C%20ED%2C%20and%20IT%20to%20take%20donations%20from%20these%20companies%20shows%20that%20the%20aim%20was%20hafta%20vasooli.%20Our%20general%20secretary%20has%20written%20to%20the%20finance%20minister%20on%20this.%20This%20has%20never%20happened%20before%20that%20private%20companies%20have%20faced%20action%20from%20probe%20agencies%20just%20to%20get%20political%20donations%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Dubious%20firms%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20letter%20to%20Sitharaman%2C%20Venugopal%20said%20that%20the%20party%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Calleging%20that%20the%20cases%20filed%2C%20or%20the%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20are%20illegal%2C%20but%20it%20does%20warrant%20an%20investigation%2C%20on%20why%20these%20%E2%80%9Cdubious%E2%80%9D%20firms%20who%20have%20ED%20cases%20against%20them%20are%20donating%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%2C%20despite%20ED%20investigation%20against%20them.%20Is%20it%20a%20mere%20coincidence%20that%20they%20are%20donating%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20after%20ED%20action%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVenugopal%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%2C%20the%20finance%20ministry%20needs%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20accountable%20for%20the%20malpractices%E2%80%9D%20adopted%20in%20%E2%80%9Cfilling%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20coffers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20letter%20Venugopal%20has%20asked%20whether%20a%20white%20paper%20will%20be%20brought%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20finances%20not%20just%20its%20sources%20but%20how%20corporate%20firms%20were%20coerced%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdonate%20by%20misusing%20investigative%20agencies.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20nothing%20to%20hide%2C%20then%20are%20you%20willing%20to%20present%20a%20point-by-point%20rebuttal%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Chronology%E2%80%99%20of%20events%20which%20led%20to%20the%20filling%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20treasury%3F%20If%20you%20are%20unwilling%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20factual%20explanation%2C%20then%20are%20you%20willing%20to%20present%20yourself%20for%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20monitored%20investigation%20in%20these%20dubious%20deals%20to%20loot%20donation%20for%20the%20BJP%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20going%20to%20the%20courts%20of%20law%20and%20to%20the%20court%20of%20people.%20We%20will%20defeat%20you%20on%20both%20sides%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708692583000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F02103902%2FFn4KRJYakAAz-Xs.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-nirmala-sitharam