ssing%26nbsp%3BFarmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20legislature%20proves%20itself%20to%20be%20incapable%20of%20safeguarding%20kisans%E2%80%99%20interests%20they%20will%20of%20course%20always%20have%20the%20sovereign%20remedy%20of%20civil%20disobedience%20and%20non-co-operation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20passage%20has%20not%20been%20authored%20by%20someone%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20in%20face%20of%20the%20Haryana%20BJP%20regime%20employing%20very%20harsh%20punitive%20measures%20against%20the%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20farmers%20are%20being%20unlawfully%20prevented%20from%20proceeding%20to%20Delhi%20and%20are%20protesting%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20for%20its%20failure%20to%20meet%20their%20demands%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20law%20for%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20some%20crops%20as%20per%20the%20formula%20of%20late%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20who%20has%20been%20chosen%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20for%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20civilian%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20words%20and%20vision%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aforementioned%20passage%20is%20from%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%202%2C%201944%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20asked%20questions%20regarding%20the%20future%20role%20of%20the%20State%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20issues%20of%20farmers%20in%20an%20interview%20by%20freedom%20fighter%20and%20peasant%20leader%20N.G.%20Ranga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20the%20peasant%20%E2%80%9Chas%20so%20to%20work%20as%20to%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20the%20landlord%20to%20exploit%20him%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Ranga%20asked%20if%20that%20included%20farmers%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3Esatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%20campaigns%20and%20the%20legislative%20and%20administrative%20reforms%20that%20the%20State%20would%20undertake%20because%20of%20%C2%A0the%20exercise%20of%20their%20franchise%20and%20political%20influence%20to%20improve%20their%20individual%20and%20collective%20conditions%20and%20minimise%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20answer%20the%20question%2C%20very%20presciently%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCivil%20disobedience%20and%20non-co-operation%20are%20designed%20for%20use%20when%20people%2C%20i.e.%2C%20the%20tillers%20of%20the%20soil%2C%20have%20no%20political%20power.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CBut%20immediately%20they%20have%20political%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnaturally%20their%20grievances%2C%20whatever%20their%20character%2C%20will%20be%20ameliorated%20through%20legislative%20channels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%2C%20however%2C%20was%20very%20much%20conscious%20of%20the%20possibilities%20when%20the%20farmers%20would%20be%20bereft%20of%20any%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20he%20cautioned%20that%20in%20case%20the%20peasants%20would%20not%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20primacy%20to%20their%20voices%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20interests%20of%20the%20tiller%20of%20the%20soil%20will%20need%20close%20watching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20proceeded%20to%20add%20very%20forcefully%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20legislature%20proves%20itself%20to%20be%20incapable%20of%20safeguarding%20%3Cem%3Ekisans%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20interests%20they%20will%20of%20course%20always%20have%20the%20sovereign%20remedy%20of%20civil%20disobedience%20and%20non-co-operation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20is%20not%20paper%20legislation%20nor%20brave%20words%20or%20fiery%20speeches%2C%20but%20the%20power%20of%20non-violent%20organisation%2C%20discipline%20and%20sacrifice%20that%20constitutes%20the%20real%20bulwark%20of%20the%20people%20against%20injustice%20or%20oppression%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20%E2%80%9Csovereign%20remedy%20%C2%A0of%20civil%20disobedience%20and%20non-co-operation%E2%80%9D%20got%20%C2%A0vey%20vividly%20reflected%20in%20the%20year-long%20peaceful%20and%20non-violent%20movement%20of%20farmers%20in%202021%20in%20response%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20farm%20laws%20by%20Parliament%20without%20consulting%20the%20farmers%20and%20dispensing%20%C2%A0the%20actual%20voting%20process%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20Constitution.%20That%20historic%20movement%20forced%20Modi%20regime%20to%20repeal%20those%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20again%20the%20farmers%20are%20resorting%20to%20the%20movement%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi%20and%20exercise%20their%20constitutional%20right%20to%20protest%20so%20that%20their%20demands%20are%20met%20and%20a%20law%20is%20enacted%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20MSP.%20Brutal%20resistance%20to%20that%20movement%20by%20the%20%C2%A0BJP%20regime%20in%20Haryana%20has%20resulted%20in%2C%20%C2%A0as%20per%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-bring-bulldozers-earth-moving-machines-to-shambhu-border-in-bid-to-restart-protest-march%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%C2%A0injury%20to%20many%20farmers%2C%20loss%20of%20%C2%A0eye%20sight%20to%20several%20of%20them%20and%20deaths%20to%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20words%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20not%20paper%20legislation%20nor%20brave%20words%20or%20fiery%20speeches%2C%20but%20the%20power%20of%20non-violent%20organisation%2C%20discipline%20and%20sacrifice%20that%20constitutes%20the%20real%20bulwark%20of%20the%20people%20against%20injustice%20or%20oppression%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20farmers%20as%20they%20have%20appealed%20to%20their%20fellow%20participants%20to%20remain%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%20must%20be%20mindful%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20none%20of%20the%20farmers%20or%20farm%20leaders%20have%20been%20reported%20to%20have%20invoked%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20their%20agitation%20%E2%80%93%20launched%2079%20years%20after%20what%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20to%20Ranga%20in%20that%20interview%20%E2%80%93%20spirit%20and%20resolute%20action%20animates%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20takes%20pride%20in%20telling%20foreign%20dignitaries%20that%20he%20hails%20from%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%20Ke%20Desh%E2%80%9D%20(the%20country%20of%20Gandhi)%2C%20so%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20words%20and%20vision%20and%20pay%20heed%20to%20the%20legitimate%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gandhi%20stated%20that%20non-cooperation%20and%20civil%20disobedience%20constituted%20%C2%A0sovereign%20remedies%2C%20Ambedkar%20in%20early%201940s%20gave%20a%20stirring%20slogan%3A%20%E2%80%9CEducate%2C%20Agitate%20and%20Organise%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20very%20sarcastically%20used%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CAndolonjeevi%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20those%20who%20earn%20through%20agitation%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20was%20at%20its%20peak%20in%202022.%20It%20was%20an%20offence%20to%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20vision%20embodied%20in%20the%20slogan%20which%20has%20been%20described%20by%20professor%20Amartya%20Sen%20as%20the%20key%20to%20deepen%20public%20reasoning%20for%20the%20sustenance%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20and%20Ambedkar%20are%20being%20assaulted%20by%20the%20forceful%20suppression%20of%20the%20movement%20