e%20Stadium.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20our%20team%20and%20we%20had%20to%20take%20him%20off%20the%20boundary%20because%20he%20was%20Mumbai's%20boy%2C%20playing%20against%20Mumbai%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20getting%20booed%20by%20the%20Wankhede%20crowd.%20So%20we%20put%20him%20back%20inside%20the%20circle%20because%20it%20was%20not%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema%20as%20the%20IPL%202024%20schedule%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20feels%20it%20would%20be%20fun%20if%20the%20fans%20decide%20to%20jeer%20Hardik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20Hardik%20Pandya%20goes%20to%20Mumbai%20after%20winning%20the%20championship%20once%2C%20leading%20the%20team%20to%20the%20final%20the%20next%20time.%20And%20not%20just%20that%20but%20choosing%20to%20leave%20the%20franchise.%20If%20there%20isn't%20any%20heartburn%20in%20the%20public%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20if%20they%20don't%20feel%20hurt%2C%20where%20is%20the%20fun%3F%20I%20am%20expecting.%20No%2C%20I%20am%20hoping%20-%20don't%20tell%20anyone%20-%20that%20Hardik%20goes%20for%20the%20toss%20and%20people%20go%20'Boo'.%20That's%20where%20the%20league%20matures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708689840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fb9ckpi0g_hardik-pandya-bcci_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwant-hardik-pandya-to-get-booed-in-ahmedabad-ex-india-stars-big-ipl-2024-take-5112140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20cricketer%20Aakash%20Chopra%20wants%20Hardik%20Pandya%20to%20be%20booed%20when%20he%20plays%20in%20Ahmedabad%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C