%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finteragencystandingcommittee.org%2Finter-agency-standing-committee%2Fstatement-principals-inter-agency-standing-committee-civilians-gaza-extreme-peril-while-world%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%98death%20blow%E2%80%99%20to%20aid%20efforts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20particularly%20dire%20in%20Rafah%2C%20at%20the%20far%20south%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRafah%2C%20the%20latest%20destination%20for%20well%20over%20one%20million%20displaced%2C%20hungry%20and%20traumatised%20people%20crammed%20into%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20land%2C%20has%20become%20another%20battleground%20in%20this%20brutal%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IASC%20heads%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%20escalation%20of%20violence%20in%20this%20densely%20populated%20area%20would%20cause%20mass%20casualties.%20It%20could%20also%20deal%20a%20death%20blow%20to%20a%20humanitarian%20response%20that%20is%20already%20on%20its%20knees%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarians%20at%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IASC%20principals%20highlighted%20the%20risks%20aid%20workers%20face%20daily%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20help%20people%20in%20desperate%20need%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20can%20%E2%80%9Conly%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHumanitarian%20workers%2C%20themselves%20displaced%20and%20facing%20shelling%2C%20death%2C%20movement%20restrictions%20and%20a%20breakdown%20of%20civil%20order%2C%20continue%20efforts%20to%20deliver%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20faced%20with%20so%20many%20obstacles%20%E2%80%93%20including%20safety%20and%20movement%20restrictions%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20only%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20essentials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principals%20underscored%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20humanitarian%20response%20will%20make%20up%20for%20the%20months%20of%20deprivation%20that%20families%20in%20Gaza%20have%20endured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20salvage%20the%20humanitarian%20operation%20so%20that%20we%20can%20provide%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20bare%20essentials%3A%20medicine%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20food%20and%20shelter%20as%20temperatures%20plummet%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%2C%20they%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%2010%20indispensable%20elements%3A%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%3B%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%3B%20immediate%20release%20of%20hostages%3B%20reliable%20entry%20points%20for%20aid%3B%20security%20assurances%20and%20unimpeded%20access%3B%20a%20functioning%20humanitarian%20notification%20system%3B%20roads%20cleared%20of%20explosive%20ordnance%3B%20and%20a%20stable%20communication%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20they%20called%20for%20the%20UN%20agency%20assisting%20Palestine%20refugees%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20receive%20the%20resources%20it%20needs%20to%20provide%20life-saving%20assistance%20as%20well%20as%20a%20halt%20to%20campaigns%20seeking%20to%20discredit%20the%20UN%20and%20NGOs%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20save%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20calling%20on%20Israel%20to%20fulfil%20its%20legal%20obligation%2C%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20and%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20to%20provide%20food%20and%20medical%20supplies%20and%20facilitate%20aid%20operations%2C%20and%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20to%20prevent%20an%20even%20worse%20catastrophe%20from%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20humanitarian%20leaders%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%2