s%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F02%2F22%2Fukraine-war-pentagon-lessons-learned%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStacie%20Pettyjohn%2C%20director%20of%20the%20defense%20program%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20a%20New%20American%20Security%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20the%20conflict%20has%20complicated%20long-held%20ideas%20that%20expensive%2C%20precision-guided%20weapons%20were%20key%20to%20winning%20US%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS-made%20Himars%20or%20Excalibur%20shells%2C%20which%20are%20guided%20to%20their%20targets%20using%20GPS%2C%20have%20proven%20vulnerable%20to%20Russian%20electronic%20warfare%20units%2C%20which%20scramble%20their%20signals%20and%20send%20them%20off%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPettyjohn%20told%20the%20Post%20that%20the%20US%20has%20almost%20certainly%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20now%20using%20older%20artillery%20which%20are%20guided%20to%20their%20targets%20using%20sensors%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHimars%20rockets%20cost%20around%20%24240%2C000%20each%2C%20and%20in%202022%20were%20deployed%20effectively%20by%20Ukraine%20to%20take%20out%20Russian%20targets%20behind%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20precision%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20leaked%20US%20intelligence%20documents%20last%20year%20indicated%20concerns%20that%20Russia%20had%20found%20ways%20to%20target%20them%20using%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20and%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuk.news.yahoo.com%2Funrealistic-us-expectations-helped-doom-150230043.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20of%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20summer%20their%20impact%20was%20blunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20instead%20used%20relatively%20cheap%20drones%20to%20identify%20targets%20for%20missile%20strikes.%20These%20weapons%20are%20not%20as%20vulnerable%20to%20electronic%20warfare%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProblems%20with%20implementing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-right-to-drop-western-tactics-fight-russia-like-it-knows-isw-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20tactics%20have%20also%20been%20exposed%20during%20the%20war%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Ukrainian%20troops%20seeking%20to%20unsuccessfully%20use%20NATO%20maneuver%20tactics%20to%20break%20through%20Russian%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Post%2C%20lessons%20from%20Ukraine%20will%20inform%20the%20US'%20next%20National%20Defense%20Strategy%2C%20with%20analysts%20examining%20ground%20warfare%2C%20information%20warfare%2C%20long-range%20fire%20capability%2C%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showed-us-precision-missiles-not-effective-russia-report-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708687900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d89dd2ce7f1785b2e35f55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showed-us-precision-missiles-not-effective-russia-report-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Expensive%20precision-guided%20US%20missiles%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20electronic%20jamming%2C%20forcing%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20reconsider%20its%20plans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showed-us-precision-missiles-not-effective-russia-report-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Economy%3A%20Down%20the%20Rabbit%20Hole%20and%20Beyond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23160306%2Fprasoon-srivastav-vDfkrGeRXRE-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20significant%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20world%20will%20be%20watching%20as%20the%20largest%20democratic%20festival%20plays%20itself%20out.%20This%20will%20undoubtedly%20have%20profound%20implications%20for%20the%20geopolitical%20order%2C%20perhaps%20even%20more%20so%20than%20the%20US%20presidential%20elections.%20The%20world%20knows%20China%E2%80%99s%20economy%20is%20faltering%3B%20therefore%2C%20it%20will%20closely%20look%20towards%20India%20as%20the%20next%20big%20economic%20force.%20There%20has%20been%20growing%20optimism%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%2C%20but%20there%20is%20one%20state%20that%20is%20pulling%20India%20down.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(UP)%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20states%2C%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20poorly%20performing%20economies%20in%20the%20north%20and%20the%20east%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20recorded%20a%20per%20capita%20Net%20State%20Domestic%20Product%20of%20Rs%2070%2C792%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%202021-22.%20With%20a%20population%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20200%20million%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economic%20disparity%20becomes%20stark.%20Despite%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20economy%20teetering%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20collapse%20due%20to%20democratic%20setbacks%20and%20sluggish%20growth%2C%20its%20per%20capita%20income%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20World%20Bank%20data%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FNY.GDP.PCAP.CD%3Flocations%3DPK%5C%22%3Estands%20at%20%241%2C588.9%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20double%20that%20of%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20know%20this%20grim%20reality%3A%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20not%20only%20trails%20behind%20Pakistan%20but%20also%20lags%20behind%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20renowned%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20poorest%20regions.%20World%20Bank%20Open%20Data%20indicates%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20(excluding%20high%20income)%20per%20capita%20income%20at%20current%20US%24%20is%20%241700.1%20in%202022.%20While%20some%20economists%20argue%20that%20per%20capita%20income%20alone%20fails%20to%20fully%20encapsulate%20a%20region%E2%80%99s%20economic%20standing%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20undeniable%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20economic%20condition%20falls%20significantly%20short%20of%20optimal%20levels.%20For%20example%2C%20Noida%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20increasing%20the%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20UP.%20The%20per%20capita%20income%20simply%20does%20not%20mean%20all%20citizens%20of%20UP%20are%20earning%20Rs%2070%2C792%20per%20year.%20Per%20capita%20income%20is%20calculated%20by%20taking%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20total%20income%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20total%20population%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20flaw%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20economy%20lies%20in%20its%20entrenched%20feudal%20system%2C%20where%20the%20state%20lords%20over%20cattle%2C%20women%2C%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20minorities.%20The%20pervasive%20presence%20of%20the%20so-called%20mafia%20raj%2C%20along%20with%20frequent%20brutalities%20such%20as%20gang%20rape%20and%20violence%2C%20has%20tainted%20UP%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20Consequently%2C%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20convenes%20an%20investor%20summit%2C%20prominent%20business%20leaders%20may%20attend%20and%20sign%20Memorandums%20of%20Understanding%2C%20yet%20the%20conversion%20rate%20remains%20abysmal.%20In%20essence%2C%20these%20investors%2C%20gripped%20by%20apprehension%20regarding%20the%20current%20administration%2C%20may%20momentarily%20commit%2C%20but%20they%20rarely%20follow%20through%20with%20the%20initiation%20or%20actualisation%20of%20commercial%20projects%20in%20UP.%20The%20share%20of%20industrial%20sector%20in%20gross%20value%20added%20has%20been%20decreasing.%20From%202012-17%2C%20the%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20industrial%20sector%20has%20been%209.9%25%20and%20from%202017-22%2C%20it%20declined%20to%20a%20mere%200.6%25.%20In%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20factories%2C%20Bihar%20saw%20a%20100.4%25%20increase%2C%20Haryana%20saw%20a%20159%25%20increase%2C%20Assam%20saw%20a%20200%25%20increase%20while%20UP%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20only%2069%25%20from%20the%20period%202004-05%20to%202019-20.%20The%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20failure%20to%20redistribute%20land%20and%20dismal%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20apparently%20made%20UP%20an%20economic%20wasteland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20facet%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20predicament%20manifests%20in%20the%20relentless%20scourge%20of%20poverty.%20The%20state%20has%20nearly%2023%25%20of%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20Just%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20three%20districts%20of%20UP%20namely%20Bahraich%2C%20Balrampur%2C%20Shravasti%20were%20in%20the%20headlines%20for%20recording%20a%2070%25%20poverty%20rate.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-08%2FIndia-National-Multidimentional-Poverty-Index-2023.pdf%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20Bahraich%20has%20more%2050%25%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20life%20expectancy%2C%20at%2066%20years%2C%20parallels%20that%20of%20African%20nations%20like%20Ethiopia%20and%20Gabon.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2Fscripts%2FAnnualPublications.aspx%3Fhead%3DHandbook%2Bof%2BStatistics%2Bon%2BIndian%2BStates%5C%22%3ERBI%20Handbook%20of%20Indian%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%2038%20per%201%2C000%20in%202020%2C%20the%20maternal%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%20167%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20and%2045.6%25%20of%20pregnant%20women%20aged%20between%2015-45%20and%2066%25%20of%20children%20of%20aged%20between%206-59%20months%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%3Eare%20anaemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20touted%20%E2%80%9Cdemographic%20dividend%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20grotesque%20reality%20is%20when%2050.4%25%20of%20the%20female%20population%20aged%20between%2015-49%20years%20are%20anaemic%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20any%20dividend%20is%20risible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20delve%20into%20the%20growth%20rate.%20The%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20has%20made%20the%20bold%20claim%20of%20a%20%241%20trillion%20economy.%20It%20is%20conventionally%20believed%20that%20states%20with%20a%20lower%20initial%20economic%20base%20possess%20higher%20potential%20for%20growth.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20poorer%20a%20state%2C%20the%20faster%20it%20can%20advance%20economically%2C%20thereby%20gaining%20increased%20access%20to%20funds%20within%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-economy-comparison-with-tamil-nadu-south-india%2Farticle67821390.ece%5C%22%3EFor%20example%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UP%20receives%20Rs%202.73%20back%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20while%20Tamil%20Nadu%20receives%20only%2029%20paisa%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union.%20Perhaps%20an%20argument%20could%20be%20made%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20working%20more%20towards%20funding%20the%20freebies%20of%20UP%2C%20but%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20objectivity%2C%20I%20would%20focus%20solely%20on%20UP.%20The%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Fups-gsdp-shrinks-5-9-per-cent-in-202021-101632161467657.html%5C%22%3EUP%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20State%20Domestic%20Product%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20current%20prices%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fdid-up-economy-do-better-under-akhilesh-than-yogi-a-data-check-on-states-1-trillion-ambition%2F1627925%2F%5C%22%3E%20has%20been%208.28%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20period%202016-17%20to%202021-22%2C%20as%20per%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Economics%20and%20Statistics%2C%20GOUP%20(Government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh).%20To%20achieve%20a%20%241%20trillion%20target%20in%20five%20years%2C%20UP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-election-adityanath-economic-performance%5C%22%3Eneeds%20to%20grow%20by%2032%25%20per%20annum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20having%20the%20audacity%20of%20ambition%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20spaceships%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20lit%20up%20by%20candles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lamentable%20part%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20that%20the%20voters%20are%20completely%20agnostic%20about%20the%20democratic%20power%20they%20posses%20to%20bring%20in%20an%20economic%20transformation.%20The%20poor%20voters%20are%20failing%20to%20grasp%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20voting%20for%20forces%20that%20are%20further%20disenfranchising%20them.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Futtar-pradesh-began-declining-after-1980s-old-industrial-cities-played-big-role%2F710784%2F%5C%22%3EUP%20has%20become%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20purgatory%20of%20prosperity%20and%20a%20geography%20of%20maladies.%20The%20economy%20cannot%20be%20drastically%20upscaled%20unless%20there%20is%20massive%20democratic%20reform%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20steady%20shrinkage%20of%20democratic%20spaces%2C%20laceration%20of%20institutional%20autonomy%2C%20the%20focus%20on%20cults%20need%20to%20stop.%20Income%2C%20quality%20of%20living%20needs%20to%20be%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20discourse%20replacing%20caste%20and%20cult.%20In%20a%20conservative%20democratic%20milieu%2C%20any%20hope%20for%20economic%20resurgence%20remains%20futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESnehasis%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20data%20science%20enthusiast%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20drawing%20insights%20from%20political%20econ