0great%20campaign%20against%20injustice%20to%20an%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nath%20made%20headlines%20recently%20over%20speculation%20that%20he%20could%20join%20the%20BJP%20but%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sign%20of%20him%20switching%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speculation%20gained%20momentum%20after%20a%20post%20shared%20by%20former%20Congress%20leader%20and%20BJP%20State%20Spokesperson%20Narendra%20Saluja%20showed%20a%20picture%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20with%20Nakul%20Nath%2C%20captioned%20'Jai%20Shree%20Ram'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20his%20plans%20to%20switch%20sides%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20said%20the%20media%20would%20be%20informed%20%26quot%3Bif%20there%20is%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20all%20getting%20excited%3F%20It%20is%20not%20about%20denying.%20I%20will%20inform%20you%20all%20if%20there%20is%20something%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%20amid%20media%20reports%20and%20speculation%20of%20his%20switch%2C%20Mr%20Nath%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20affirming%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ideology%20of%20Congress%20is%20the%20ideology%20of%20truth%2C%20religion%20and%20justice.%20There%20is%20equal%20place%20and%20respect%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20Congress%20for%20all%20religions%2C%20castes%2C%20regions%2C%20languages%20and%20ideas%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20138-year%20history%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%20has%20been%20spent%20in%20struggle%20and%20service.%20In%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20movement%2C%20there%20was%20a%20competition%20among%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20serve%20the%20country%20in%20the%20struggle%20against%20dictatorship.%20Nation%20building%20is%20the%20only%20aim%20of%20Congress%20after%20independence%26quot%