realist%20phone%20calls%20to%20scammers%20to%20bait%20them%20into%20ridiculous%20situations%20using%20voice%20mods%20%5Bvoice-altering%20software%5D%2C%20fake%20banks%2C%20and%20fake%20gift%20card%20redeems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20content%20creator%20who%20is%20apparently%20in%20his%2030s%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F22%2Fus-news%2Finternet-scammers-who-target-americans-caught-on-camera%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20revealed%20that%20he%20finds%20the%20scammers%20by%20Googling%20phrases%20like%20%26quot%3BZelle%20support%26quot%3B%20and%20calling%20their%201-800%20numbers%2C%20or%20sometimes%20they%20contact%20%26quot%3BNeld%26quot%3B%2C%20thinking%20they%20are%20targeting%20an%20old%20woman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fjye8B6wiAfI%3Fsi%3DavC6ICLYfJUvqPsB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20videos%2C%20he%20is%20often%20asked%20by%20the%20scammers%20to%20go%20to%20a%20CVS%20or%20Walmart%20and%20purchase%20gift%20cards%20worth%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20He%20fakes%20doing%20all%20this%20and%20then%20sends%20the%20scammers%20the%20details.%20The%20YouTuber%20also%20keeps%20them%20online%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20playing%20along%20with%20their%20scams.%20He%20drives%20them%20crazy%20by%20responding%20slowly%20and%20stupidly%20to%20their%20demands.%20%26quot%3BNeld%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20the%20scammers%20usually%20pretend%20to%20be%20American%20or%20Mexican%2C%20with%20names%20such%20as%20Thomas%20Wayne%20and%20Brian%20Collins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%5C%22%3EUS%20Man%20Makes%20%242%20Million%20By%20Eavesdropping%20On%20Wife's%20Office%20Calls%20During%20WFH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20worn%20down%20some%20to%20the%20point%20of%20tears%2C%20swearing%20they%20will%20give%20up%20their%20criminality%20and%20go%20straight%20if%20he'd%20only%20leave%20them%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3BNeld%26quot%3B%20insider%20told%20The%20%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20usually%20happens%20only%20after%20he's%20actually%20hacked%20their%20computers%20and%20downloaded%20or%20destroyed%20all%20of%20their%20data%20by%20installing%20a%20very%20dangerous%20computer%20virus%20on%20the%20scammers'%20computers%2C%20gained%20control%20of%20their%20webcams%20and%20livestreamed%20video%20of%20them%20to%20the%20world%2C%20embarrassing%20them%20publicly%20and%20threatening%20to%20contact%20their%20innocent%20families%2C%20revealing%20their%20criminal%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20brilliant%20and%20has%20a%20truly%20dark%20sense%20of%20humor.%20While%20he%20won't%20discuss%20it%2C%20he%20does%20report%20some%20of%20his%20investigations%20to%20authorities%20in%20the%20US%20and%20in%20India%2C%20in%20hopes%20authorities%20will%20make%20arrests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20usually%20takes%20over%20the%20scammers'%20webcams%20and%20reveals%20to%20the%20scammers%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bknows%20precisely%20where%20they%20are%20working%20from%2C%20frequently%20in%20Indian%20cities%2C%20and%20sometimes%20in%20West%20African%20countries%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20tells%20them%20that%20he%20can%20see%20their%20group%20chats%2C%20and%20even%20in%20one%20case%20a%20scammer%20sliding%20into%20a%20woman's%20direct%20messages%20(DMs).%20He%20then%20unleashes%20powerful%20viruses%20on%20their%20computers%2C%20ruining%20their%20ability%20to%20scam%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPost%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20the%20American%20Association%20of%20Retired%20Persons%20(AARP)%20warned%20last%20year%20that%20Americans%20over%2060%20were%20scammed%20of%20%2428.3%20billion%20every%20year%2C%20with%20just%201%20in%2010%20of%20the%20scams%20reported%20to%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708685520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0a7t0c9c_computer-generic_625x300_04_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-exposes-scammers-on-camera-after-posing-as-80-year-old-woman-5112884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20YouTuber%20with%20over%2090%2C000%20subscribers%20is%20giving%20scammers%20a%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20medicine%20by%20exposing%20them%20on%20camera%20after%20posing%20as%20a%20vulnerable%20grandmother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-exposes-scammers-on-camera-after-posing-as-80-year-old-woman-5112884%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-exposes-scammers-on-camera-after-posing-as-80-year-old-woman-5112884%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fyoutuber-exposes-scammers-on-camera-after-posing-as-80-year-old-woman-5112884%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana%20compares%20Oppenheimer%20with%20a%20sage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708685088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107943293%2Cimgsize-82790.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkangana-ranaut-on-j-robert-oppenheimer-his-cosmic-engagement-reflected-in-appearance%2Farticleshow%2F107943324.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107943324.cms%5C%22%20hspac