ission%20said%20on%20Thursday.%E2%80%8B%20Loudon's%20wife%20worked%20as%20a%20mergers%20and%20acquisition%20manager%20at%20BP%2C%20a%20London-based%20oil%20and%20gas%20conglomerate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhow-this-us-man-made-2-million-after-overhearing-wifes-office-calls-during-wfh%2Farticleshow%2F107942559.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20India-China%20Ties%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20Talks%20About%20%26quot%3BMind%20Games%20Played%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Friday%20said%20arriving%20at%20an%20equilibrium%20and%20maintaining%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20challenges%26quot%3B%20for%20India-China%20ties%20even%20as%20he%20asserted%20that%20the%20immediate%20issue%20at%20hand%20was%20Beijing's%20departure%20from%20laid%20down%20norms%20triggering%20the%20border%20row%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interactive%20session%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogue%2C%20he%20cautioned%20against%20China's%20%26quot%3Bmind%20game%26quot%3B%20to%20restrict%20the%20issues%20under%20the%20bilateral%20framework%20and%20said%20India%20must%20not%20forgo%20its%20rights%20to%20harness%20other%20factors%20in%20the%20world%20to%20get%20better%20terms%20on%20an%20equilibrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20there%20would%20be%20a%20period%20when%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20will%20be%20flattening%20out%20and%20India%20will%20be%20growing%20and%20referred%20to%20projections%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%20that%20suggested%20that%20by%202075%2C%20both%20countries%20could%20end%20up%20as%20USD%2050%20trillion%20plus%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20should%20be%20confident%20enough%20to%20%26quot%3Bleverage%26quot%3B%20the%20international%20system%20to%20create%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20possible%20outcome%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20when%20asked%20whether%20there%20would%20be%20a%20settling%20point%20between%20China%20and%20India%20and%20would%20the%20two%20countries%20finally%20find%20an%20equilibrium%20or%20a%20balance%20in%20their%20frosty%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20is%20the%20immediate%20issue%20which%20is%3A%20From%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20we%20had%20an%20understanding%20on%20the%20border%20precisely%20because%20it%20suited%20both%20of%20us.%20Now%20there%20was%20a%20departure%20after%20almost%2030%20years.%20A%20departure%20on%20their%20side%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20they%20behaved%20on%20the%20border.%20And%20there%20was%20a%20pushback%20from%20our%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20arriving%20at%20an%20equilibrium%2C%20then%20maintaining%20those%20and%20refreshing%20those%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20both%20countries.%20It%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20%26quot%3Bmind%20games%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20played%20which%20would%20be%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20between%20the%20two%20of%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20190%20odd%20countries%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20our%20relationship.%20That%20will%20be%20the%20mind%20game%20which%20will%20be%20played.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20we%20should%20play%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20if%20there%20are%20other%20factors%20out%20there%20in%20the%20world%20which%20can%20be%20harnessed%20by%20me%20to%20get%20better%20terms%20on%20an%20equilibrium%2C%20then%20why%20should%20I%20forgo%20that%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20I%20say%20think%20through%20your%20own%20solution%2C%20do%20not