dian%20nationals%20to%20exercise%20due%20caution%20and%20stay%20away%20from%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgovt-in-talks-with-russian-authorities-for-early-discharge-of-indians-forced-to-fight-in-russia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Exercise%20caution'%3A%20Govt%20to%20Indians%20drafted%20into%20Russia%20army%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708683559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107943082%2Cimgsize-36330.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fexercise-caution-govt-warns-indians-trapped-in-private-army-in-russia%2Farticleshow%2F107942405.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aware%20that%20a%20few%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20signed%20up%20for%20support%20jobs%20with%20the%20Russian%20army.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20has%20regularly%20taken%20up%20this%20matter%20with%20the%20relevant%20Russian%20authorities%20for%20their%20early%20discharge.%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20official%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaishwal%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fexercise-caution-govt-warns-indians-trapped-in-private-army-in-russia%2Farticleshow%2F107942405.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20Presents%20First%20Post-Gaza%20War%20Plan%2C%20Proposes%20Complete%20Control%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20presented%20a%20%26quot%3Bday%20after%26quot%3B%20plan%20for%20Gaza%2C%20his%20first%20official%20proposal%20for%20when%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20territory%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20document%2C%20presented%20to%20members%20of%20Israel's%20security%20cabinet%20on%20Thursday%20and%20seen%20by%20Reuters%20on%20Friday%2C%20Israel%20would%20maintain%20security%20control%20over%20all%20land%20west%20of%20Jordan%2C%20including%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%20-%20territories%20where%20the%20Palestinians%20want%20to%20create%20an%20independent%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long-term%20goals%20listed%2C%20Netanayhu%20rejects%20the%20%26quot%3Bunilateral%20recognition%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%20He%20says%20a%20settlement%20with%20the%20Palestinians%20will%20only%20be%20achieved%20through%20direct%20negotiations%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20-%20but%20it%20did%20not%20name%20who%20the%20Palestinian%20party%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20Netanyahu%20outlines%20demilitarization%20and%20deradicalization%20as%20goals%20to%20be%20achieved%20in%20the%20medium%20term.%20He%20does%20not%20elaborate%20on%20when%20that%20intermediary%20stage%20would%20begin%20or%20how%20long%20it%20would%20last.%20But%20he%20conditions%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20laid%20to%20waste%20by%20Israel's%20offensive%2C%20on%20its%20complete%20demilitarization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20proposes%20Israel%20have%20a%20presence%20on%20the%20Gaza-Egypt%20border%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20enclave%20and%20cooperates%20with%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States%20in%20that%20area%20to%20prevent%20smuggling%20attempts%2C%20including%20at%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20replace%20Hamas%20rule%20in%20Gaza%20while%20maintaining%20public%20order%2C%20Netanyahu%20suggests%20working%20with%20local%20representatives%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20not%20affiliated%20with%20terrorist%20countries%20or%20groups%20and%20are%20not%20financially%20supported%20by%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20calls%20for%20shutting%20down%20the%20U.N.%20Palestinian%20refugees%20agency%20UNRWA%20and%20replacing%20it%20with%20other%20international%20aid%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prime%20minister's%20document%20of%20principles%20reflects%20broad%20public%20consensus%20over%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20war%20and%20for%20replacing%20Hamas%20rule%20in%20Gaza%20with%20a%20civilian%20alternative%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20was%20distributed%20to%20security%20cabinet%20members%20to%20start%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20Oct.%207%20in%20which%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20253%20taken%20hostage%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVowing%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20Israel%20has%20responded%20with%20an%20air%20and%20ground%20assault%20on%20blockaded%20Gaza%20that%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2029%2C400%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities.%20The%20offensive%20has%20displaced%20most%20of%20the%20territory's%20population%20and%20caused%20widespread%20hunger%20and%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesman%20for%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20Nabil%20Abu%20Rudeineh%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Netanyahu's%20proposal%20was%20doomed%20to%20fail%2C%20as%20were%20any%20Israeli%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20geographic%20and%20demographic%20realities%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20world%20is%20genuinely%20interested%20in%20having%20security%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20must%20end%20Israel's%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20land%20and%20recognise%20an%20independent%20Palestinian%20state%20with%20Jerusalem%20as%20its%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20revived%20international%20calls%20-%20including%20Israel's%20main%20backer%20the%20United%20States%20-%20for%20the%20so-called%20two-state%20solution%20as%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20for%20resolving%20the%20decades%20long%20Israel-Palestinian%20conflict.%20However%2C%20a%20number%20of%20senior%20Israeli%20politicians%20oppose%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20has%20long%20been%20a%20core%20Western%20policy%20in%20the%20region%20but%20little%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20on%20achieving%20Palestinian%20statehood%20since%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Oslo%20Accords%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708683480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpk2blch4_benjamin-netanyahu_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-presents-first-post-gaza-war-plan-proposes-complete-control-5112504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20presented%20a%20%26quot%3Bday%20after%26quot%3B%20plan%20for%20Gaza%2C%20his%20first%20official%20proposal%20for%20when%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20territory%20ends.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-presents-first-post-gaza-war-plan-proposes-complete-control-5112504%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-presents-first-post-gaza-war-plan-proposes-complete-control-5112504%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-presents-first-post-gaza-war-plan-proposes-complete-control-5112504%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir's%20niece%20Samara's%20antics%20is%20talk%20of%20town%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17