vind%20Kejriwal%20if%20Party%20Proceeds%20With%20Congress%20for%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23151422%2FScreenshot-2024-02-23-at-3.13.48.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20through%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20if%20the%20party%20proceeds%20with%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today%2C%20February%2023%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20and%20AAP%20MLA%20Atishi%20said%20that%20the%20party%20has%20learnt%20from%20%E2%80%9Creliable%20sources%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20CBI%20is%20planning%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20seeing%20for%20the%20last%20two%20to%20two-and-half%20months%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20seven%20times.%20But%20now%20the%20BJP-led%20centre%20has%20understood%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20through%20the%20ED.%20So%20now%20the%20BJP-led%20centre%20is%20bringing%20the%20CBI%20and%20planning%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20press%20address%20by%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20in%20which%20the%20party%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20been%20informed%20that%20if%20it%20ties%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAtishi%E2%80%99s%20press%20conferences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Febr