C%20arrest%20all%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20hang%20us%20but%20we%20will%20not%20be%20scared%20of%20your%20threats.%20We%20have%20been%20fighting%20for%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20come%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20have%20reached%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20reaching%20seat%20sharing%20agreement%20across%20states%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Goa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20final%20shape%20to%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20come%20only%20weeks%20after%20the%20AAP%20throwing%20the%20gauntlet%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20offering%20only%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-throws-down-gauntlet-to-congress-seat-sharing-delay%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20capital%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cdeserve%20a%20single%20seat%20on%20merit%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20national%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20admitted%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20seat%20sharing%20talks%2C%20its%20Delhi%20unit%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cenergised%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalks%20in%20final%20stage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPathak%20said%20today%20that%20the%20announcement%20on%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20relating%20to%20all%20states%20will%20be%20done%20together%20and%20the%20talks%20are%20at%20%E2%80%9Cfinal%20stage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20announcement%20will%20be%20done%20very%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPathak%20added%20that%20if%20Kejriwal%20is%20arrested%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctsunami%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country%20as%20people%20will%20take%20to%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20a%20tsunami%20in%20the%20country%20and%20all%20well%20meaning%20people%20will%20take%20to%20the%20roads%20and%20all%20their%20political%20calculations%20which%20they%20think%20will%20work%20if%20Kejriwal%20is%20arrested%20will%20be%20fall%20flat.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20political%20pundits%2C%20you%20are%20not%20dealing%20with%20any%20political%20party%20but%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20take%20on%20AAP.%20They%20are%20saying%20leave%20the%20alliance%20or%20we%20will%20arrest%20Kejriwal.%20We%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20arrests%2C%20if%20we%20were%20then%20so%20many%20of%20our%20leaders%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20in%20jail.%20We%20will%20not%20be%20scared.%20We%20are%20in%20the%20alliance%20not%20for%20our%20personal%20profit%20but%20for%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharadwaj%20said%20that%20the%20haste%20with%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20use%20central%20agencies%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20shows%20its%20%E2%80%9Cnervousness%E2%80%9D%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20despite%20claims%20from%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20will%20cross%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20nervousness%20is%20showing.%20So%20they%20have%20decided%20to%20forget%20ED%2C%20and%20tell%20the%20CBI%20to%20quickly%20arrest%20Kejriwal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(BJP)%20think%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20come%20together%2C%20then%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20difficulties%20will%20increase%20in%20those%20states%20where%20our%20alliance%20is%20there.%20They%20are%20making%20big%20statements%20of%20crossing%20400%20seats.%20The%20person%20who%20is%20promising%20to%20cross%20400%20seats%20won%E2%80%99t%20send%20CBI%20to%20an%20elderly%20former%20governor.%20These%20are%20not%20signs%20of%20%E2%80%98400%20%3Cem%3Epar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%20Ask%20any%20political%20scientist.%20One%20who%20is%20crossing%20400%20seats%20shows%20signs%20of%20love%2C%20not%20of%20fear%20and%20loss.%20We%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20BJP%20that%20you%20can%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20if%20you%20want%2C%20but%20Kejriwal%20and%20Congress%20alliance%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20formed%20and%20will%20not%20stop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708681580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23151422%2FScreenshot-2024-02-23-at-3.13.48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-bjp-congress-arrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20come%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20have%20reached%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20reaching%20seat%20sharing%20agreement%20in%20states%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Goa%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20an%20announcement%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-bjp-congress-arrest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Sudharma%3A%20A%20Mysuru%20Family's%20Decades-Long%20Journey%20To%20Keep%20Sanskrit%20Alive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20was%20walking%20down%20a%20narrow%20street%20in%20Mysuru's%20Agrahara%20locality%20when%20my%20phone's%20map%20misled%20me%2C%20announcing%20I%20had%20reached%20the%20office%20of%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20only%20daily%20newspaper%20in%20the%20world%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsanskrit%5C%22%3ESanskrit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20dead%20end%2C%20with%20houses%20stacked%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20all%20arou