20also%20published%20the%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanskrit-is-language-of-progress-and-identity-pm-modi-in-chitrakoot-4520263%5C%22%3ESanskrit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecalendar%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20inspiration%20comes%20from%20the%20legacy%20left%20behind%20by%20my%20father-in-law%20and%20carried%20forward%20by%20my%20husband.%20In%20all%20of%20India%2C%20he%20was%20the%20one%20to%20start%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20his%20strength%20and%20vision.%20I%20joined%20this%20mission%20and%20realised%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20duty%20but%20a%20part%20of%20who%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jayalakshmi.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThey%20were%20not%20just%20preserving%20a%20newspaper%20but%20nurturing%20a%20cultural%20treasure.%26quot%3B%20Despite%20initial%20scepticism%20about%20its%20viability%2C%20Pandit%20Iyengar's%20commitment%20to%20adapting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Futtar-pradesh-government-makes-amendment-to-project-alankar-to-renovate-old-sanskrit-school-building-4508858%5C%22%3ESanskrit%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20modern%20times%20led%20to%20the%20adoption%20of%20new%20words%20for%20contemporary%20concepts%2C%20making%20the%20language%20accessible%20and%20practical.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20through%20the%20corridors%20of%20%3Cem%3ESudharma's%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoffice%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20it%20hit%20me%20that%20this%20isn't%20just%20about%20a%20newspaper.%20It's%20a%20fight%20to%20keep%20a%20piece%20of%20our%20past%20alive.%20I%20was%20stepping%20into%20a%20story%20that%20began%20over%20half%20a%20century%20ago.%20Despite%20all%20odds%2C%20financial%20hurdles%2C%20and%20the%20onslaught%20of%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Estands%20firm%2C%20a%20small%20paper%20with%20a%20big%20heart.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20can't%20join%20the%20army%20or%20contribute%20in%20other%20conventional%20ways%2C%20running%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20promoting%20Sanskrit%20is%20my%20way%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20nation.%20It's%20not%20solely%20about%20making%20a%20profit%3B%20it's%20about%20giving%20back%20to%20our%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20playing%20a%20part%20in%20preserving%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jayalakshmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20I%20looked%20around%20at%20the%20stacks%20of%20paper%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20the%20ink%2C%20and%20the%20old%20printing%20machine%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20wonder%3A%20what%20is%20the%20place%20of%20an%20ancient%20Indian%20language%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESanskrit%20In%20The%20Age%20Of%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20are%20you%20keeping%20Sanskrit%20alive%3F%20I%20asked.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSudharma%20isn't%20about%20keeping%20Sanskrit%20alive!%26quot%3B%20Jayalakshmi%20stressed.%20She%20shared%20an%20anecdote%20about%20an%2080-year-old%20linguist%20from%20Varanasi%20who%20knew%20over%20a%20hundred%20languages%20and%20was%20visiting%20%3Cem%3ESudharma's%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoffice.%20A%20language%20survives%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20spoken%20or%20understood%20by%20even%20one%20person%2C%20the%20linguist%20mentioned.%20%26quot%3BEven%20those%20who%20may%20not%20consciously%20know%20Sanskrit%20are%20exposed%20to%20it%20through%20prayers%20and%20rituals.%20For%20instance%2C%20commonly%20recited%20prayers%20and%20verses%20are%20in%20Sanskrit%2C%20making%20the%20language%20a%20part%20of%20everyday%20life%20for%20many%20Indians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reframed%20my%20understanding%20of%20%3Cem%3ESudharma's%20%3C%2Fem%3Erole%20-%20not%20as%20a%20preserver%20of%20a%20dying%20language%20but%20as%20a%20platform%20celebrating%20a%20language%20that%20is%20very%20much%20alive%20in%20the%20hearts%20and%20homes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20about%20making%20profits%2C%20ensuring%20that%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Esurvives%20and%20supports%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20those%20running%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMoney%20vs%20Purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20profit%20versus%20cultural%20contribution%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20individual%20perspective.%20Of%20course%2C%20financial%20stability%20is%20important%20for%20everyone%2C%20and%20commercial%20aspects%20can't%20be%20ignored.%20But%20in%20India's%20context%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%20contributing%20something%20meaningful%20to%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayalakshmi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20complex.%20Jayalakshmi's%20insights%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20this%20struggle.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20an%20edition%20of%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Enewspaper%20could%20take%20six%20days%20to%20reach%20readers%20in%20places%20like%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20was%20acceptable.%20But%20now%2C%20people%20want%20immediate%20news.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20demand%20for%20instant%20information%20is%20changing%20journalism.%20It's%20becoming%20harder%20to%20maintain%20readership%20because%20everyone%20has%20a%20mobile%20phone.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Easuras%20%3C%2Fem%3E(devils)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBeyond%20The%20Newsprint%3A%20A%20Cultural%20Crusade%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20several%20news%20reports%20have%20flagged%20the%20crises%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20facing.%20Jayalakshmi%20acknowledges%20the%20challenges%20but%20stands%20by%20her%20belief%20that%20the%20newspaper%20isn't%20going%20to%20shut%20down.%20%26quot%3BWe%20never%20considered%20shutting%20down%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20even%20during%20tough%20times.%20Every%20day%20brought%20new%20challenges%2C%20but%20we%20never%20let%20negativity%20set%20in.%20There%20were%20rumours%20about%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eclosing%2C%20but%20they%20were%20unfounded.%20We%20always%20aimed%20to%20keep%20the%20paper%20running%20and%20even%20expand%20it.%20Our%20message%20has%20always%20been%20clear%20in%20the%20media%3B%20we're%20committed%20to%20continuing%20and%20growing%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20does%20a%20tiny%20newspaper%20find%20the%20tenacity%20to%20keep%20at%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20motivation%20comes%20from%20understanding%20the%20importance%20of%20our%20work%20and%20its%20role%20in%20education.%20Parents%20usually%20want%20their%20children%20to%20become%20engineers%2C%20doctors%2C%20or%20IAS%20officers%2C%20and%20few%20aspire%20for%20their%20children%20to%20become%20Sanskrit%20scholars.%20But%20we%20see%20that%20even%20engineers%20are%20now%20learning%20Sanskrit%20and%20becoming%20scholars%2C%20even%20though%20the%20number%20may%20be%20small.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMore%20Than%20A%20Newspaper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20media%20landscape%2C%20there's%20often%20a%20rush%20to%20find%20the%20most%20financially%20viable%20model%2C%20a%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20profits%20overshadowing%20purpose.%20But%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eteaches%20us%20a%20different%20lesson.%20Here's%20a%20media%20model%20that%20doesn't%20rely%20solely%20on%20its%20balance%20sheets.%20Instead%2C%20it%20anchors%20itself%20firmly%20in%20its%20purpose%2C%20staying%20true%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20mission.%26quot%3BThe%20journey%20of%20keeping%20Sanskrit%20alive%20is%20long%2C%20but%20just%20as%20radio%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20centuries%2C%20so%20too%20will%20the%20approach%20to%20Sanskrit%20and%20its%20study.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESudharma's%20%3C%2Fem%3Eapproach%20to%20preserving%20Sanskrit%20goes%20beyond%20just%20publishing%20a%20newspaper.%20They're%20using%20every%20tool%3A%20printed%20calendars%2C%20books%2C%20community%20involvement%2C%20and%20offline%20events.%20It's%20not%20about%20survival%20at%20any%20cost.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20a%20thoughtful%20blend%20of%20traditional%20and%20modern%20methods%2C%20all%20aimed%20at%20keeping%20their%20mission%20alive.%20%26quot%3BWe%20aim%20to%20provide%20information%20about%20our%20culture%2C%20geography%2C%20language%2C%20and%20more%20through%20these%20calendars.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20mountains%20in%20our%20culture%2C%20drawing%20from%20various%20scriptures.%20These%20calendars%20promote%20our%20language%20and%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayalakshmi%20Iyengar%20tells%20me%2C%20flipping%20pages%20of%20a%20newly%20printed%20calendar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20engaging%20people%20with%20printed%20calendars%20that%20tell%20more%20than%20just%20dates%20and%20books%20and%20delve%20into%20the%20richness%20of%20Sanskrit%20literature%2C%20they're%20making%20ancient%20wisdom%20accessible%20and%20relevant.%20The%20community%20plays%20a%20big%20role%2C%20too.%20%3Cem%3ESudharma%20%3C%2Fem%3Etries%20to%20foster%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%20around%20the%20language%20through%20local%20events%20and%20gatherings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ELanguage%20No%20Bar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudharma%20isn't%20alone%20in%20its%20quest.%20Sanskrit%20is%20making%20a%20comeback%20worldwide%2C%20from%20Germany's%20universities%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20Mysuru.%20%26quot%3BSanskrit%20and%20yoga%20are%20intertwined%2C%20and%20as%20awareness%20grows%2C%20more%20people%20are%20drawn%20to%20learn%20about%20our%20culture%20and%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayalakshmi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20connection%20between%20language%20and%20lifestyle%20is%20seen%20across%20the%20world.%20In%20Germany%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Sanskrit's%20appeal%20has%20grown%20remarkably.%20While%20only%20four%20universities%20teach%20Sanskrit%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%20boasts%2014.%20This%20interest%20isn't%20a%20recent%20trend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20remember%20how%20my%20late%20father%2C%20a%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20who%20also%20spoke%20German%2C%20often%20marvelled%20at%20the%20deep%20connections%20between%20the%20two%20languages%2C%20both%20culturally%20and%20etymologically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shared%20journey%20shows%20how%20people%20and%20institutions%2C%20separated%20by%20thousands%20of%20miles%2C%20can%20be%20connected%20by%20their%20love%20for%20a%20language.%20As%20I%20wrapped%20up%20my%20conversation%20with%20Jayalakshmi%20and%20prepared%20to%20leave%2C%20she%20handed%20me%20a%20few%20fruits%20-%20a%20banana%2C%20an%20apple%2C%20and%20an%20orange.%20Along%20with%20her%20%26quot%3BNamaskara%26quot%3B%20once%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20down%20the%20street%20with%20the%20fruits%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20feel%20enveloped%20by%20the%20warmth%20of%20the%20culture%20around%20me.%20It%20was%20a%20subtle%20reminder%20of%20how%20this%20rich%20past%20touches%20and%20shapes%20us%20in%20many%2C%20often%20unnoticed%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20FactorDaily.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708681500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F29d9qmr_sudharma_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsudharma-a-mysuru-familys-decades-long-journey-to-keep-sanskrit-alive-5112453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20does%20it%20take%20for%20the%20world's%20only%20Sanskrit%20newspaper%20to%20stay%20relevant%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%3F%20Sheer%20grit%20and%20unflinching%20resolve%2C%20above%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsudharma-a-mysuru-familys-decades-long-journey-to-keep-sanskrit-alive-5112453%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20young%20Bollywood%20star%20taking%20on%20Hollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708681388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14B7C%2Fproduction%2F_132706848_gettyimages-1590030046.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68338730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actress%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20adored%20by%20fans%20in%20India%2C%20is%20making%20her%20mark%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68338730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68338730.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68338730.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smita%20Bharadwaj%20seeks%20help%20of%20the%20court%20for%20sale%20of%20Nitish's%20property%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708681338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107941004%2Cimgsize-23534.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-smita-bharadwaj-seeks-help-of-the-court-for-sale-of-nitish-bharadwajs-property%2Farticleshow%2F107940829.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20divorce%20between%20Smita%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Nitish%20Bharadwaj%20is%20complicated.%20Nitish%20accused%20Smita%20of%20harassment%20and%20kidnapping%20their%20daughters.%20Smita%20seeks%20court%20help%20to%20sell%20Nitish's%20property%20for%20child%20maintenance.%20She%20is%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20Nitish%20in%20the%20family%20court%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-smita-bharadwaj-seeks-help-of-the-court-for-sale-of-nitish-bharadwajs-property%2Farticleshow%2F107940829.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Money%2C%20Power%2C%20Politics%20and%20Electoral%20Bonds%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Preserves%20Sanctity%20of%20Electoral%20Process%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15213318%2FThe-unemployment-situation-2.gif%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20verdict%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20on%20the%20key%20questions%20related%20to%20transparency%20in%20financial%20contribution%20to%20political%20parties.%20Central%20to%20this%20verdict%20is%20not%20only%20an%20affirmation%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20but%20also%20the%20influence%20of%20money%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20electoral%20process%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20in%20fostering%20participatory%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20deliberated%20on%20the%20challenge%20to%20a%20set%20of%20parliamentary%20laws%20which%20introduced%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20(%E2%80%9Cscheme%E2%80%9D)%20in%20January%202018%20and%20provided%20for%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20financial%20contributions%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20and%20enabled%20unlimited%20corporate%20funding%20to%20political%20parties%20by%20removing%20cap%20on%20the%20funding%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20primary%20issues%20were%20deliberated.%20First%2C%20whether%20the%20non-disclosure%20of%20information%20regarding%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%20violated%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20of%20citizen%20as%20enshrined%20in%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Second%2C%20whether%20unlimited%20corporate%20funding%20to%20political%20parties%20infringed%20upon%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20thereby%20violating%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERight%20to%20information%20of%20voter%20and%20participatory%20democracy%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20issue%2C%20the%20court%20examined%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20right%20to%20information%20extends%20to%20financial%20contribution%20made%20to%20political%20parties.%20While%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20court%20analysed%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20scope%20of%20Right%20to%20Information%20in%20two%20distinct%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20the%20scope%20was%20limited%20to%20open%20government%20and%20transparency.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20the%20court%20progressively%20expanded%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20recognised%20the%20role%20of%20information%20in%20debate%2C%20discussion%2C%20and%20fostering%20democratic%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20first%20and%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20laid%20the%20foundational%20framework%20for%20the%20court%20to%20guarantee%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voter%20about%20the%20contesting%20candidates%20background%20including%20their%20criminal%20past%20in%20%3Cem%3EUnion%20of%20India%20v%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%202002%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EPUCL%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%202003%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20first%20issue%2C%20the%20court%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20political%20parties%20are%20relevant%20political%20units%20and%20are%20central%20to%20the%20democratic%20electoral%20process.%20Consequently%2C%20it%20affirmed%20that%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%20extends%20to%20political%20parties%20given%20their%20significance%20in%20shaping%20the%20electoral%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opinion%20of%20the%20court%20was%20based%20on%20the%20assessment%20of%20the%20prominence%20accorded%20to%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20constitutional%20framework%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20tenth%20schedule%2C%20and%20their%20position%20within%20the%20legal%20framework%20related%20to%20the%20election%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%20includes%20information%20about%20financial%20contribution%20to%20a%20political%20party.%20The%20court%20made%20a%20comprehensive%20analysis%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20political%20inequality%20and%20economic%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20constitution%20mandates%20political%20equality%20by%20ensuring%20equal%20value%20and%20voice%20of%20each%20vote%20to%20influence%20government%20decisions%20and%20policy%2C%20economic%20inequality%20can%20still%20perpetuate%20political%20inequality.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20economic%20inequality%20allows%20the%20wealthy%20individuals%20and%20corporate%20to%20%E2%80%98get%20seat%20at%20the%20table%E2%80%99%20and%20influence%20not%20only%20the%20policy%20decisions%20but%20also%20the%20electoral%20outcome%20by%20virtue%20of%20their%20financial%20contributions%20to%20the%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20progressive%20reading%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20by%20the%20court%20to%20include%20financial%20contribution%20to%20political%20parties%20resulted%20from%20the%20recognition%20that%20such%20transparency%20enables%20voters%20to%20evaluate%20any%20potential%20quid%20pro%20quo%20between%20contributors%20and%20political%20parties.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20facilitates%20an%20assessment%20of%20the%20influence%20of%20money%20on%20policy%20decisions%20and%20electoral%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felectoral-bonds-narendra-modi-rbi%5C%22%3EModi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Tryst%20with%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Should%20Neither%20Be%20Forgotten%20Nor%20Forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnlimited%20funding%20and%20electoral%20corruption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20addressed%20a%20crucial%20issue%20regarding%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20unlimited%20corporate%20funding%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20which%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20amending%20Section%20182%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act%202013%2C%20that%20removed%20the%20cap%20on%20corporate%20donations%20to%20political%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20lies%20the%20significant%20role%20of%20money%20in%20electoral%20politics%20as%20emphasised%20by%20the%20court%20throughout%20its%20judgment.%20Recognising%20the%20nexus%20between%20money%2C%20power%20and%20politics%2C%20the%20court%20highlighted%20its%20influence%20on%20electoral%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20in%20his%20concurring%20opinion%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20influence%20of%20money%20itself%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20and%20undermines%20the%20quality%20and%20integrity%20of%20governmental%20decision-making%20processes%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20question%20of%20unlimited%20funding%2C%20the%20court%20asserted%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20within%20an%20electoral%20democracy%2C%20emphasising%20the%20sanctity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20as%20previously%20established%20in%20cases%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20v.%20Raj%20Narain%201975%20and%20PUCL%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%202013%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20unlimited%20corporate%20funding%20authorises%20companies%20to%20exert%20unrestrained%20influence%20over%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20fostering%20corruption%20in%20electoral%20financing.%20Thus%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20such%20practice%20violates%20the%20fundamental%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20is%20inherently%20arbitrary%20and%20violates%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20informational%20privacy%20of%20donors%20vs%20Right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20argument%20on%20informational%20privacy%20for%20donors%2C%20the%20court%20relied%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EK.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%202017%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20held%20that%20the%20Constitution%20recognises%20the%20right%20to%20informational%20privacy%20of%20political%20affiliation%2C%20which%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20financial%20contributions%20made%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20privacy%20regarding%20political%20affiliation%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20to%20exercising%20the%20freedom%20of%20political%20expression.%20The%20lack%20of%20privacy%20in%20political%20affiliation%20and%20the%20disclosure%20of%20information%20about%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20political%20beliefs%20could%20lead%20to%20disproportionate%20effects%2C%20such%20as%20voter%20surveillance%20and%20the%20suppression%20of%20dissenting%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20competing%20interests%20of%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voter%20and%20the%20informational%20privacy%20of%20donor%2C%20the%20court%20applied%20double%20proportionality%20standards%20%3Cem%3E(test%20applied%20by%20court%20to%20balance%20two%20conflicting%20fundamental%20right)%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20balance%20both%20the%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20blanket%20non-disclosure%20of%20information%20as%20envisaged%20under%20the%20scheme%20heavily%20favoured%20informational%20privacy%20and%20did%20not%20adequately%20balance%20the%20competing%20interests.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20court%20held%20that%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%20cannot%20be%20restricted%20based%20on%20the%20informational%20privacy%20of%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20defense%20that%20the%20scheme%20curbs%20the%20circulation%20of%20black%20money%20in%20electoral%20funding%20by%20incentivising%20donations%20through%20the%20banking%20channel%2C%20the%20court%20affirmed%20that%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20can%20be%20curtailed%20only%20on%20the%20limited%20grounds%20of%20restriction%20provided%20under%20Article%2019(2).%20The%20purpose%20of%20curbing%20black%20money%20cannot%20be%20traced%20to%20any%20of%20the%20grounds%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20court%20rejected%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fillicit-bonds-scrapped-peoples-right-to-know-inseparable-from-free-and-fair-elections%5C%22%3E%20Illicit%20Bonds%20Scrapped%3A%20People%E2%80%99s%20Right%20to%20Know%20Inseparable%20From%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20violation%20of%20privacy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20strong%20assertion%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20election%2C%20and%20the%20role%20of%20right%20to%20information%20in%20nurturing%20participatory%20democracy%2C%20this%20verdict%20highlights%20two%20distinctive%20features.%20Firstly%2C%20it%20extends%20the%20right%20to%20information%20to%20political%20parties.%20This%20ruling%20would%20impact%20the%20issue%20originating%20from%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%20outright%20refusal%20to%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%202005.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20acknowledges%20the%20informational%20privacy%20of%20donors%2C%20including%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20opens%20the%20door%20for%20divergence%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20interpreting%20informational%20privacy%20to%20donors%20in%20view%20of%20the%20concurring%20opinion%20of%20Justice%20Khanna%20who%20slightly%20differed%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20affairs%20of%20public%20company%20(or%20even%20a%20private%20company)%20are%20open%20to%20the%20shareholders%20and%20public%2C%20thus%20claim%20of%20the%20violation%20of%20privacy%20lacks%20substantial%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20reinstates%20faith%20in%20constitutional%20principles%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20through%20its%20interpretative%20exercise%20and%20provides%20clearer%20standards%20for%20the%20legislature%E2%80%99s%20adherence.%20It%20also%20reinforces%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20RTI%20as%20an%20important%20instrument%20for%20upholding%20our%20democratic%20values%20and%20expands%20on%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20scope%20of%20informational%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYaqoob%20Alam%20is%20a%20lawyer%20at%20Saraf%20and%20Partners.%20He%20works%20on%20diverse%20issues%20related%20to%20technology%20law%20and%20public%20policy.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708681289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmoney-power-politics-and-electoral-bonds-supreme-court-preserves-sanctity-of-electoral-process%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20the%20competing%20interests%20of%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voter%20and%20the%20informational%20privacy%20of%20donor%2C%20the%20court%20applied%20double%20proportionality%20standards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmoney-power-politics-and-electoral-bonds-supreme-court-preserves-sanctity-of-electoral-process%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Supreme%20Court%20defends%20ruling%20on%20minorities%20after%20backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708680986000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107940865%2Cimgsize-20598.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-supreme-court-defends-ruling-on-minorities-after-backlash%2Farticleshow%2F107940868.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%