esofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fweb-stories%2Fchristopher-nolan-and-cillian-murphys-oppenheimer-how-and-when-to-watch-on-ott%2Farticleshow%2F107940734.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22M%C3%A9decins%20Sans%20Fronti%C3%A8res%20Condemns%20Killing%20of%20Staff%20Members'%20Family%20in%20Israeli%20Offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14112003%2Fpal-is-conf-gaza_0.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20strongly%20worded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msf.org%2Fmsf-strongly-condemns-deadly-israeli-attack-msf-shelter-gaza%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20M%C3%A9decins%20Sans%20Fronti%C3%A8res%20(MSF)%20has%20condemned%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20of%20its%20staff%20members%E2%80%99%20family%20members%20during%20an%20Israeli%20offensive%20in%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20Khan%20Younis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%2C%20which%20occurred%20late%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20February%2020%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20a%20daughter-in-law%20and%20wife%20of%20an%20MSF%20colleague%2C%20with%20six%20others%20sustaining%20injuries%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsraeli%20forces%2C%20during%20a%20military%20operation%20in%20Al-Mawasi%2C%20targeted%20a%20house%20sheltering%20MSF%20colleagues%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20attack%20extended%20beyond%20the%20residence%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msf.org%2Fmsf-strongly-condemns-deadly-israeli-attack-msf-shelter-gaza%5C%22%3Ebullets%20hitting%20the%20clearly%20marked%20MSF%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20organisation%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20shelling%20in%20the%20area%20caused%20a%20delay%20of%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20for%20ambulance%20teams%20to%20reach%20the%20site.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20wounded%20were%20transported%20to%20the%20International%20Medical%20Corps%20Field%20hospital%20in%20Rafah%2C%20with%20some%20sustaining%20burn%20injuries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeinie%20Nicolai%2C%20MSF%20General%20Director%2C%20expressed%20outrage%20and%20deep%20sadness%20over%20the%20killings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20outraged%20and%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20these%20killings%E2%80%A6On%20the%20same%20day%20the%20United%20States%20chose%20to%20veto%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20two%20daughters%20saw%20their%20mother%20and%20sister-in-law%20killed%20by%20an%20Israeli%20tank%20shell.%20These%20killings%20underscore%20the%20grim%20reality%20that%20nowhere%20in%20Gaza%20is%20safe%2C%20that%20promises%20of%20safe%20areas%20are%20empty%20and%20deconfliction%20mechanisms%20unreliable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20force%20being%20used%20in%20densely%20populated%20urban%20environments%20is%20staggering%2C%20and%20targeting%20a%20building%20knowing%20it%20is%20full%20of%20humanitarian%20workers%20and%20their%20families%20is%20unconscionable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nicolai%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20attack%2C%2064%20people%20were%20sheltering%20in%20the%20house%20and%20Israeli%20forces%20were%20regularly%20informed%20of%20MSF%20teams%E2%80%99%20presence%20in%20specific%20locations.%20Despite%20this%2C%20no%20evacuation%20orders%20were%20issued%20before%20the%20strike.%20MSF%20has%20sough%20further%20explanation%20from%20Israeli%20authorities%20over%20the%20unprovoked%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20incident%20follows%20a%20previous%20attack%20on%20an%20MSF%20shelter%20in%20Rafah.%20MSF%20teams%20are%20currently%20providing%20support%20to%20those%20who%20survived%20the%20Al-Mawasi%20attack%20and%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20were%20killed.%20The%20organisation%20has%20lost%20five%20staff%20members%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%2C%20it%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMSF%20also%20reiterated%20its%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20and%20sustained%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2029%2C000%20people%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20killed%20while%20many%20more%20have%20been%20injured%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%20on%20October%207%20last%20year.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Director-General%2C%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%2C%20called%20Gaza%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20zone%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20recent%20press%20briefing%20in%20Geneva%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20figure%20will%20rise%20the%20longer%20the%20war%20goes%20on%20and%20supplies%20%5Bare%5D%20interrupted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708680602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14112003%2Fpal-is-conf-gaza_0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmedecins-sans-frontieres-condemns-killing-of-staff-members-family-in-israeli-offensive%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%2C%20during%20a%20military%20operation%20in%20Al-Mawasi%2C%20targeted%20a%20house%20sheltering%20MSF%20workers%20and%20their%20families%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20the%20daughter-in-law%20and%20wife%20of%20an%20MSF%20worker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmedecins-sans-frontieres-condemns-killing-of-staff-members-family-in-israeli-offensive%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Triptii%20recreated%20Kartik%E2%80%99s%20monologue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708680470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%