20introduced%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20pilot%20project%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20implemented%20this%20year%2C%20aims%20to%20assess%20the%20viability%20of%20OBE%20in%20selected%20schools%20and%20subjects%2C%20notably%20English%2C%20Mathematics%2C%20and%20Science%20for%20lower%20classes%20and%20English%2C%20Mathematics%2C%20and%20Biology%20for%20higher%20classes.%20While%20proponents%20highlight%20the%20potential%20benefits%20of%20reducing%20student%20stress%20and%20mitigating%20unfair%20practices%20such%20as%20cheating%2C%20critics%20voice%20apprehensions%20regarding%20infrastructure%20readiness%20and%20the%20practicality%20of%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20emphasise%20that%20while%20OBE%20may%20foster%20critical%20thinking%20and%20problem-solving%20skills%2C%20its%20successful%20execution%20hinges%20upon%20adequate%20preparation%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20estimating%20a%20timeline%20of%205%20to%208%20years%20for%20full%20implementation%20across%20classes%2010%20to%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20require%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20empower%20our%20paper%20setters%20to%20create%20such%20types%20of%20questions%2C%20which%20can%20then%20be%20implemented%20in%20very%20limited%20subjects.%20After%205-8%20years%2C%20we%20can%20implement%20them%20in%20Class%2010%20and%20Class%2012%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20CBSE%20chairman%20Ashok%20Ganguly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20parents%20express%20concerns%20about%20potential%20limitations%20for%20their%20children%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20necessity%20of%20purchasing%20specific%20textbooks%20and%20the%20burden%20of%20note-taking.%20This%20apprehension%20underscores%20broader%20considerations%20about%20accessibility%20and%20equity%20in%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPilot%20Run%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20is%20planning%20a%20pilot%20run%20of%20open-book%20assessments%20in%20selected%20schools%2C%20targeting%20subjects%20-English%2C%20Mathematics%2C%20and%20Science%20for%20Classes%209%20and%2010%2C%20and%20English%2C%20Mathematics%2C%20and%20Biology%20for%20Classes%2011%20and%2012.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20gauge%20the%20time%20taken%20by%20students%20to%20complete%20these%20tests%20and%20gather%20feedback%20from%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpen%20Book%20Examinations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20common%20perception%2C%20open-book%20exams%20aren't%20necessarily%20easier%20than%20closed-book%20exams.%20They%20require%20students%20to%20demonstrate%20comprehension%2C%20analysis%2C%20and%20application%20of%20concepts%20rather%20than%20relying%20solely%20on%20memorisation.%20The%20focus%20lies%20on%20assessing%20higher-order%20thinking%20skills%2C%20critical%20analysis%2C%20and%20problem-solving%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPilot%20implementation%20and%20decision-making%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20pilot%20is%20scheduled%20for%20November-December%2C%20with%20the%20Board%20intending%20to%20evaluate%20its%20efficacy%20before%20adoption.%20The%20assessment%20will%20emphasise%20higher-order%20thinking%20skills%20and%20creative%20problem-solving%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsultation%20and%20preparation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20plans%20to%20finalise%20the%20design%20and%20development%20of%20the%20OBE%20pilot%20by%20June%2C%20seeking%20guidance%20from%20Delhi%20University%20(DU)%2C%20which%20pioneered%20open%20book%20tests%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20The%20initiative%20faced%20initial%20opposition%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20equitable%20access%20for%20underprivileged%20and%20visually%20challenged%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearnings%20from%20past%20experiments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20had%20previously%20experimented%20with%20an%20Open%20Text-Based%20Assessment%20(OTBA)%20format%20but%20discontinued%20it%20due%20to%20unfavourable%20feedback.%20Drawing%20from%20this%20experience%2C%20discussions%20within%20the%20curriculum%20committee%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20high-quality%20textbooks%20and%20suggested%20involving%20teachers%20in%20the%20initial%20OBE%20trials%20to%20ensure%20standards%20akin%20to%20advanced%20placement%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708679880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F10ku2omo_board-exam_625x300_20_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fas-cbse-proposes-open-book-exams-for-class-9-12-parents-concerned-5112184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CBSE%20Open%20Book%20Exams%3A%20Parents%20express%20concerns%20about%20potential%20limitations%20for%20their%20children%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20necessity%20of%20purchasing%20specific%20textbooks%20and%20the%20burden%20of%20note-taking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fas-cbse-proposes-open-book-exams-for-class-9-12-parents-concerned-5112184%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fas-cbse-proposes-open-book-exams-for-class-9-12-parents-concerned-5112184%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fas-cbse-proposes-open-book-exams-for-class-9-12-parents-concerned-5112184%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sony%20Pictures%20Television%20Announces%20%E2%80%98La%20Academia%2C%E2%80%99%20Its%20First%20Spanish-Language%20Spain-Produced%20Series%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708679553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FACDM_CAP03_Still-copia.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235920173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20milestone%20move%2C%20Sony%20Pictures%20Television