2FSatya_Pal_Malik_02_cropped-e1566998525756.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20crucial%202024%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20the%20country%20is%20witnessing%20a%20barrage%20of%20raids%20by%20the%20central%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20aimed%20particularly%20at%20those%20who%20have%20questioned%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2022%2C%20the%20South%20Delhi%20residence%20of%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20was%20raided%20too.%20Malik%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20on%20various%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20about%20100%20personnel%20from%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20went%20to%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Som%20Vihar%2C%20and%2029%20other%20premises%2C%20on%20February%2022%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Kiru%20Hydropower%20project%20over%20River%20Chenab%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Malik%20had%20spoken%20about%20corruption%20in%20the%20multi-crore%20project%2C%20and%20had%20claimed%20that%20while%20being%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20he%20was%20also%20offered%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%20300%20crore%20to%20clear%20two%20files%20of%20which%20one%20was%20on%20this%20project.%20He%20had%20served%20in%20that%20post%20between%20August%2023%2C%202018%20and%20October%2030%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20X%20after%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20raid%2C%20Malik%20termed%20Modi%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdictator%E2%80%9D%2C%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20dictator%20is%20trying%20to%20scare%20me%20by%20misusing%20government%20agencies.%20I%20am%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%3B%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20scared%20and%20bow%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsatya-pal-malik-kashmir-governor-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3Eexplosive%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Malik%20had%20also%20accused%20Modi%20of%20asking%20him%20to%20keep%20quiet%20about%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20the%20CRPF%20personnel%20in%20Pulwama%20in%202019.%20A%20terror%20attack%20had%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%2040%20CRPF%20personnel%20and%20injured%20several.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20then%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20a%20big%20convoy%20never%20goes%20by%20road%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20tragedy%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20had%20the%20ministry%20headed%20by%20top%20BJP%20leader%20Rajnath%20Singh%20agreed%20to%20provide%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20told%20it%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20the%20evening%20(of%20February%2014%2C%202019)%20that%20this%20has%20happened%20due%20to%20our%20fault.%20Had%20we%20given%20the%20aircraft%2C%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened.%20To%20which%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20should%20keep%20quiet%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20had%20also%20said%20this%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20outspoken%20Malik%20later%20called%20for%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20February%2022%20CBI%20raid%20was%20carried%20out%20when%20Malik%20was%20admitted%20in%20a%20Delhi%20hospital.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20his%20hospital%20bed%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20raided%20because%20I%20support%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cause%3B%20have%20questioned%20corruption%3B%20and%20the%20mishandling%20that%20had%20led%20to%20the%202019%20Pulwama%20tragedy%20where%20so%20many%20of%20our%20CRPF%20personnel%20lost%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20were%20you%20when%20the%20CBI%20raid%20was%20conducted%20in%20your%20house%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20at%20the%20hospital%20for%20the%20last%20five%20days%20due%20to%20a%20severe%20chest%20infection.%20I%20am%20diabetic%3B%20the%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20had%20also%20gone%20up%20quite%20a%20bit%20and%20therefore%2C%20I%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised.%20The%20CBI%20personnel%20came%20to%20my%20Som%20Vihar%20flat%3B%20I%20said%20what%20will%20they%20find%20except%20my%20clothes%20there%3F%20They%20also%20raided%20my%20driver%20and%20the%20assistant%20and%20harassed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20fail%20to%20understand%20why%20I%20was%20raided%3B%20there%20is%20no%20FIR%20against%20me.%20Instead%20of%20probing%20those%20whom%20I%20said%20had%20tried%20to%20bribe%20me%20to%20clear%20a%20file%20on%20the%20multi-crore%20project%2C%20CBI%20is%20raiding%20the%20complainant.%20This%20means%20I%20was%20raided%20for%20raising%20a%20voice%20against%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20also%20said%20on%20X%20that%20you%20are%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20son%20and%20you%20would%20not%20be%20scared%20by%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20have%20not%20done%20any%20wrong%3B%20so%20why%20should%20I%20be%20scared%3F%20I%20support%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20cause.%20I%20am%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20raided%20also%20because%20I%20had%20questioned%20the%20Modi%20government%20about%20the%20Pulwama%20tragedy%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20told%20me%20to%20keep%20quiet%20about%20it.%20That%20I%20went%20public%20angered%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20farmers%E2%80%99%20Dilli%20Chalo%20rally%20has%20been%20stopped%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%20You%20call%20yourself%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%3B%20one%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%20has%20also%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20the%20ongoing%20protest%2C%20allegedly%20in%20police%20action.%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20earlier%20Kisan%20Andolan%2C%20the%20farmers%20were%20accused%20(by%20the%20ruling%20party)%20of%20being%20Khalistani%2C%20terrorist%2C%20anti-national.%20Finally%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20to%20take%20back%20the%20anti-farmer%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20too%2C%20everything%20possible%20is%20being%20done%20to%20show%20them%20in%20bad%20light.%20The%20young%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20death%20is%20tragic%3B%20should%20not%20have%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%2C%20like%20before%2C%20will%20have%20to%20eventually%20agree%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands.%20I%20was%20raided%20also%20because%20I%20spoke%20for%20the%20kisan%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Edehat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(hinterland).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarriers%20have%20been%20put%20at%20both%20the%20Delhi-Haryana%20and%20Delhi-Uttar%20Pradesh%20borders%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20too%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20can%E2%80%99t%20enter%20the%20National%20Capital%20to%20raise%20their%20voice%20at%20the%20Ram%20Lila%20Maidan.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20arrangements%20look%20as%20if%20these%20are%20India-Pakistan%20and%20India-China%20borders.%20I%20would%20say%2C%20had%20such%20care%20been%20taken%20in%20Pulwama%20in%20February%202019%20by%20the%20government%2C%20so%20many%20of%20our%20army%20men%20would%20not%20have%20been%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708679485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F28185118%2FSatya_Pal_Malik_02_cropped-e1566998525756.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fi-was-raided-because-i-questioned-modi-govt-on-pulwama-tragedy-satya-pal-malik%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20governor%20spoke%20to%20The%20Wire%20from%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20when%20the%20CBI%20raided%20his%20residence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in