ated%20in%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20Industrial%20Ward%20at%20around%209%20pm.%20First%2C%20members%20of%20his%20family%20were%20locked%20up.%20Then%2C%20he%20was%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assailants%20shot%20Khampei%20from%20point%20blank%20range%20on%20his%20chest%20and%20left%20him%20outside%20the%20house%20before%20fleeing%20the%20scene.%20Soon%20after%20hearing%20the%20commotion%2C%20some%20neighbours%20rushed%20to%20the%20house%2C%20opened%20the%20doors%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Nagaland%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20police%E2%80%99s%20preliminary%20inquiry%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhampei%20died%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nearest%20primary%20health%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20reports%20said%20Tizit%20Police%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20and%20is%20investigating%20the%20murder.%20Tizit%20town%20is%20said%20to%20be%20tense%20but%20under%20control.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhampei%20had%20joined%20the%20Isak-Muivah%20faction%20of%20the%20NSCN%20in%20October%202023.%20He%20had%20been%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20NSCN%20(Khaplang)%20group%20located%20in%20Myanmar%20till%20July%202023%2C%20when%20a%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20Khaplang%20group%2C%20U%20Angmai%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fnagaland%2Fstory%2Fnagaland-nscn-yung-aung-faction-splits-appoints-ang-mai-as-new-president-607691-2023-07-02%5C%22%3Eengineered%20a%20split%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20outfit%20led%20by%20veteran%20Naga%20leader%20S.S.%20Khaplang%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20Yung%20Aung.%20U%20Angmai%20belongs%20to%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Tangshang%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20split%2C%20Khampei%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.morungexpress.com%2Fnscn-k-turned-nscn-im-kilonser-shot-dead-in-tizit%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20Khaplang%20group%20on%20health%20grounds