3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20my%20surprise%2C%20I%20found%20her%20with%20the%20lady%20sarpanch%20(elected%20head%20of%20the%20village).%20The%20baby%E2%80%99s%20head%20was%20out%20when%20she%20reached%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObstetric%20violence%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31722765%2F%5C%22%3Edefined%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0mistreatment%2C%20disrespect%20and%20abuse%20or%20dehumanised%20care%20of%20women%20during%20childbirth%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20public%20health%20problem%20that%20directly%20affects%20rates%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7462032%2F%5C%22%3Ematernal%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1016%2Fj.rhm.2016.04.004%5C%22%3EForced%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lack%20of%20consent%20for%20procedures%20such%20as%20episiotomies%20and%20vaginal%20examinations%20during%20birth%2C%20bullying%2C%20coercion%20and%20non-cooperative%20attitudes%20are%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F326469018_Domesticating_Bodies_The_Role_of_Shame_in_Obstetric_Violence%5C%22%3EGendered%20shame%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20insufficient%20pain%20relief%20and%20unethical%20medical%20practices%20are%20other%20crude%20manifestations%20of%20this%20medical%20malpractice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20there%20is%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736(22)01022-4%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Eunder-recognised%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20obstetric%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20obstetric%20practices%20mirror%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F22146035%2F%5C%22%3Eattitudes%20of%20abusive%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20that%20they%20attempt%20to%20coercively%20control%20women%20through%20manipulation%20and%20violence%2C%20name-calling%20and%20ch