0x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Vinod%20says%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20is%20between%2070%20and%2080%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20rectified%20these%20mistakes%20in%20the%20second%20batch.%20He%20bought%20another%201%2C000%20oysters%20and%20released%20them%20in%20the%20pond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20time%2C%20I%20regularly%20checked%20the%20pH%20and%20the%20temperature%20in%20the%20pond.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20pH%20should%20be%207.5%20%5Bbasic%5D%20and%20the%20temperature%20should%20be%20maintained%20between%2025%20and%2030%20degrees.%20During%20summer%2C%20the%20temperature%20shoots%20to%2050%20degrees%20in%20our%20region.%20To%20maintain%20an%20ideal%20temperature%2C%20I%20installed%20a%20green%20shade%20and%20kept%20rotating%20water%20for%203-4%20hours%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20had%20hoped%2C%20the%20success%20rate%20this%20time%20was%2070%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20this%2C%20I%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20recovered%20the%20investment%20amounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Vinod%20used%20the%20profits%20to%20expand%20pearl%20farming%20in%20four%20ponds%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20two%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B1.25%20acre%5D.%20In%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%20each%20pearl%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20was%20thrice%20the%20investment%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22120