-vladimir-kara-murza_6465382.jpg%3F20240222153950%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpale-drawn-and-in-a-siberian-prison-what-remains-of-russias-opposition-attempts-to-rally-supporters-13078390%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20remains%20of%20Russia's%20opposition%20through%20the%20stuffy%2C%20bureaucratic%20prism%20of%20a%20Moscow%20courtroom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpale-drawn-and-in-a-siberian-prison-what-remains-of-russias-opposition-attempts-to-rally-supporters-13078390%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20UPSC%20Mains%20Marksheet%E2%80%99%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20Shares%20Prep%20Lessons%20With%20Memories%20of%20Her%201st%20Failed%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20failure%20is%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20rings%20especially%20true%20for%20many%20successful%20individuals%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20civil%20services.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%3C%2Fa%3E%20exams%20stand%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20competitive%20and%20challenging%20examinations%20to%20conquer.%20Behind%20the%20triumph%20of%20many%20rank%20holders%20and%20nearly%20all%20officers%2C%20lies%20a%20compelling%20story%20of%20perseverance%20and%20resilience%20amidst%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Sonal%20Goel%20%E2%80%94%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20currently%20serving%20as%20the%20Resident%20Commissioner%20at%20Tripura%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20She%20secured%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%2013%20in%20t