atients%20have%20experienced%20positive%20results%20with%20our%20device%2C%20and%20some%20have%20even%20experienced%20a%20better%20rate%20of%20hair%20regrowth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Raghuveer%E2%80%99s%20startup%20featured%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20great%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank.%20We%20got%20three%20sharks%20on%20board%20%E2%80%94%20Aman%20Gupta%2C%20Namita%20Thapper%2C%20and%20Ritesh%20Agarwal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20deal%20itself%2C%20what%20excites%20Raghuveer%20is%20the%20success%20of%20the%20device.%20%E2%80%9CFour%20years%20ago%2C%20there%20was%20no%20clear%20solution%20available%20to%20this%20problem.%20Now%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20patients%20have%20a%20solution%20in%20at%20least%2018%20installations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20just%20a%20cosmetic%20device.%20A%20cancer%20patient%20already%20deals%20with%20a%20plethora%20of%20problems.%20Being%20able%20to%20remove%20one%20burden%20and%20add%20certain%20value%20to%20a%20cancer%20patient%E2%80%99s%20life%20gives%20me%20a%20huge%20sense%20of%20contentment.%20My%20role%20is%20small%20but%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20I%20get%20out%20of%20it%20is%20immense%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Raghuveer%20Surupa)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708524524000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20Raghuveer%20Surupa%2C%20founder%20of%20Stemtech%20Medical%20Devices%2C%20created%20the%20Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%20to%20help%20patients%20experiencing%20hair%20loss%20during%20chemotherapy.%20The%20system%2C%20designed%20to%20pro