with%20Lenovo%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kanthalloor%20Grama%20Panchayat%20President%20P%20T%20Mohandas%20was%20campaigning%20for%20elections%20in%202020%2C%20he%20saw%20huge%20sacks%20lying%20in%20several%20households.%20On%20inquiry%2C%20he%20found%20that%20each%20of%20the%20tribal%20households%20there%20had%20almost%20500%20to%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20lying%20unused.%20Reason%20%E2%80%94%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20it%20and%20used%20this%20superfood%20solely%20for%20self-consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20had%20to%20be%20done%2C%20thought%20Mohandas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20began%20seeking%20ways%20to%20sell%20the%20surplus%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20uplift%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%2C%20Lenovo%20was%20also%20exploring%20ways%20to%20integrate%20technology%20for%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare%20and%20promote%20the%20cultivation%20of%20millets%20in%20Kanthalloor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanthalloor%20was%20once%20home%20to%20over%2018%20varieties%20of%20millet%2C%20according%20to%20farmers.%20But%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20as%20people%20shifted%20towards%20consuming%20more%20rice%20and%20wheat%2C%20millet%20consumption%20gradually%20reduced%20and%20so%20did%20its%20cultivation.%20The%20village%20lost%20its%20diverse%20variety%20of%20millet%20and%20the%20number%20came%20down%20from%2018%20to%20just%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20millet%20cultivation%20in%20the%20Idukki%20district%20and%20help%20farmers%20flourish%20through%20the%20assistance%20of%20technology.%20Through%20its%20%E2%80%98Work%20for%20Humankind%E2%80%99%20initiative%2C%20the%20volunteers%20have%20helped%20reinstate%20some%20lost%20millets%2C%20bringing%20the%20millet%20variety%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20set%20up%20a%20digital%20centre%2C%20worked%20on%20the%20branding%20and%20marketing%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20processing%20unit%20%E2%80%94%20all%20to%20help%20Kanthalloor%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20restore%20its%20generational%20millet%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20about%201%2C800%20kg%20of%20six%20types%20of%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20including%20finger%20millet%2C%20barnyard%20millet%2C%20little%20millet%2C%20foxtail%20millet%2C%20proso%20millet%2C%20and%20kodo%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20cultivated%20by%2025%20farmers%20on%2015%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village.%20This%20harvest%20has%20also%20been%20processed%20and%20packaged%2C%20and%20will%20be%20sold%20through%20the%20various%20channels.%20The%20farmers%20hail%20this%20initiative%20and%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20harbinger%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20human-centric%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20were%20earlier%20growing%20millets%20only%20for%20self-consumption%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-76