egitimate%20business.%20On%20the%20entrepreneurial%20side%2C%20I%20have%20to%20sit%20with%20my%20team%20to%20assess%20the%20share%20agreements%20and%20other%20documents%20sent%20by%20the%20Sharks%E2%80%99%20teams%20as%20well.%20All%20this%20due%20diligence%20work%20will%20take%20about%20six%20months%20or%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Falwaysalittleextra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%2FDiksha%20Singhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Falittleextra.co.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%2FA%20Little%20Extra%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708005588000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_427511830_18005696192342913_3817577765527529167_n_1080-1708004227.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Relentlessly%20bullied%20as%20a%20child%2C%20Diksha%20Singhi%20overcame%20her%20trauma%20to%20become%20a%20body%20positivity%20influencer.%20Today%2C%20she%20runs%20an%20unconventional%20jewellery%20brand%20called%20'A%20Little%20Extra'%20which%20recently%20secured%20funding%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341941%2Fshark-tank-india-diksha-singhi-body-positivity-a-little-extra-jewellery-brand%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ratan%20Tata%E2%80%99s%20Rs%20165%20Cr%20Animal%20Hospital%20Inspired%20by%20His%20Own%20Struggle%20to%20Treat%20Pet%20Dog%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20Image%20Courtesy%3A%20Ratan%20Tata%2FIn